1
00:00:00,167 --> 00:00:03,836
Guys, I've got huge news.

2
00:00:04,004 --> 00:00:05,471
I think I do too.

3
00:00:05,773 --> 00:00:08,341
I saw the director's interview.

4
00:00:08,342 --> 00:00:10,912
- That's right.
- What's going on? I have no idea.

5
00:00:10,913 --> 00:00:11,778
Well,

6
00:00:12,646 --> 00:00:14,847
- we have an actual couple.
- An actual couple?

7
00:00:14,848 --> 00:00:16,549
We have a couple in real life.

8
00:00:16,550 --> 00:00:18,818
So they got caught, didn't they?

9
00:00:20,454 --> 00:00:21,508
- No, that's not it.
- I mean...

10
00:00:21,722 --> 00:00:22,889
Why do you think they got caught?

11
00:00:22,890 --> 00:00:24,857
They should be careful
when the show is still airing!

12
00:00:25,959 --> 00:00:27,794
They're not ordinary people anymore.

13
00:00:27,795 --> 00:00:28,994
That's true.

14
00:00:29,329 --> 00:00:32,631
We have a real-life couple
from this season.

15
00:00:33,100 --> 00:00:36,269
They were already together
by the time filming ended,

16
00:00:36,837 --> 00:00:37,904
and the episodes started airing.

17
00:00:37,905 --> 00:00:39,639
- Really?
- Let's give them a round of applause.

18
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:40,873
(Congratulations!)

19
00:00:40,874 --> 00:00:41,774
- Good for them!
- Who are they?

20
00:00:41,809 --> 00:00:42,876
- So that means...
- Who are they?

21
00:00:42,877 --> 00:00:45,312
It means we have one couple?

22
00:00:45,313 --> 00:00:46,579
- No.
- We don't know.

23
00:00:46,580 --> 00:00:47,680
We don't know.

24
00:00:47,981 --> 00:00:50,282
- We don't know how many there are.
- It could be five couples,

25
00:00:50,283 --> 00:00:52,886
or it could be just one couple.

26
00:00:52,887 --> 00:00:55,020
The director didn't mention the number.

27
00:00:55,021 --> 00:00:56,288
Who are they?

28
00:00:57,057 --> 00:00:59,492
Among those who get it right, five winners
will be selected by random draw...

29
00:00:59,693 --> 00:01:03,096
Give them the cards they played.
The Truth Cards.

30
00:01:03,097 --> 00:01:06,198
Or we can ask Jin Woo for vouchers...

31
00:01:06,199 --> 00:01:07,933
to his shabu-shabu restaurant.

32
00:01:08,169 --> 00:01:10,669
- Or a haircut from Yun So.
- Or a haircut.

33
00:01:10,838 --> 00:01:12,639
- We have plenty of prizes.
- I love that.

34
00:01:12,907 --> 00:01:14,643
Why is it so windy?

35
00:01:14,644 --> 00:01:15,775
(At that moment,)

36
00:01:15,776 --> 00:01:17,076
(Ji Hye arrives at the place
for her Extended Date.)

37
00:01:17,077 --> 00:01:19,345
No way. She didn't!

38
00:01:21,014 --> 00:01:23,716
(Did she also choose Jung Won?)

39
00:01:23,851 --> 00:01:26,285
There's no way we have
more women coming here, right?

40
00:01:27,688 --> 00:01:28,554
Who knows?

41
00:01:28,555 --> 00:01:30,256
- "Who knows?"
- Right.

42
00:01:30,257 --> 00:01:32,125
- It's possible.
- Right.

43
00:01:32,126 --> 00:01:33,326
Who else do we have left?

44
00:01:33,327 --> 00:01:34,594
(Tired)

45
00:01:35,529 --> 00:01:40,333
(Who is she on her way to see?)

46
00:01:40,501 --> 00:01:41,801
No. Please don't.

47
00:01:41,802 --> 00:01:42,602
No.

48
00:01:43,003 --> 00:01:46,005
If she does,
four women will have chosen Jung Won.

49
00:01:46,974 --> 00:01:50,043
I thought
Si Won would be very talkative...

50
00:01:50,177 --> 00:01:52,111
and cheerful.

51
00:01:52,479 --> 00:01:54,914
But on the date, I got the impression...

52
00:01:55,415 --> 00:01:58,684
that I wasn't very comfortable around him.

53
00:02:00,587 --> 00:02:02,421
They're just not each other's type.

54
00:02:02,422 --> 00:02:03,856
(Ji Hye didn't request an extension
of her date with Si Won.)

55
00:02:11,198 --> 00:02:12,098
Hello.

56
00:02:13,934 --> 00:02:15,067
- Why are you so surprised?
- What?

57
00:02:15,068 --> 00:02:16,802
(Ji Hye chose Jun Han.)

58
00:02:16,803 --> 00:02:18,271
- What?
- Have you been waiting long?

59
00:02:18,505 --> 00:02:19,705
(Jun Han?)

60
00:02:19,706 --> 00:02:20,606
Jun Han!

61
00:02:20,607 --> 00:02:22,741
He seems genuinely surprised.

62
00:02:22,742 --> 00:02:23,796
(Jun Han can't hide he shocked.)

63
00:02:23,797 --> 00:02:25,279
(Ji Hye's choice was Jun Han.)

64
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,345
Have you been waiting long?

65
00:02:26,346 --> 00:02:27,746
- No.
- No?

66
00:02:28,749 --> 00:02:29,949
- Wait, what?
- What do you mean?

67
00:02:30,851 --> 00:02:32,018
Is it good or bad?

68
00:02:32,219 --> 00:02:33,185
- It means good.
- Really?

69
00:02:33,253 --> 00:02:34,486
He covered his mouth with his hand.

70
00:02:34,487 --> 00:02:35,422
What?

71
00:02:35,423 --> 00:02:36,989
I love it here.

72
00:02:38,258 --> 00:02:39,091
Love it.

73
00:02:39,426 --> 00:02:40,226
Did you order something?

74
00:02:40,227 --> 00:02:41,394
No. I didn't.

75
00:02:41,734 --> 00:02:42,627
Wow.

76
00:02:43,063 --> 00:02:44,830
- What?
- This is totally unexpected.

77
00:02:44,831 --> 00:02:46,032
- Really?
- Yes.

78
00:02:48,702 --> 00:02:50,803
I really need a drink.

79
00:02:50,938 --> 00:02:52,472
Really? Then let's order some drinks.

80
00:02:52,806 --> 00:02:54,073
Let's drink soju and beer.

81
00:02:54,074 --> 00:02:55,875
Soju and beer? Then I'll just drink soju.

82
00:02:55,876 --> 00:02:57,743
- Okay.
- I feel like soju today.

83
00:02:59,546 --> 00:03:00,747
(On the date with Ju Hee this morning)

84
00:03:00,748 --> 00:03:03,349
Right. Jun Han went on a date with Ju Hee.

85
00:03:03,917 --> 00:03:07,553
(Ju Hee didn't extend her date
with Jun Han.)

86
00:03:08,689 --> 00:03:09,655
Yes.

87
00:03:09,923 --> 00:03:10,790
Oh, no.

88
00:03:11,825 --> 00:03:13,959
Okay. I understand what you mean.

89
00:03:15,395 --> 00:03:16,428
I'll get going, then.

90
00:03:18,432 --> 00:03:19,665
See you at the house.

91
00:03:19,666 --> 00:03:21,701
- See you.
- Bye.

92
00:03:21,702 --> 00:03:23,102
- Bye.
- Get back safely.

93
00:03:27,174 --> 00:03:29,308
(Jun Han was happy every moment
with Ju Hee on that date.)

94
00:03:29,309 --> 00:03:31,411
Every moment with her was just happy.

95
00:03:35,882 --> 00:03:38,050
But she didn't want to extend her date
with me.

96
00:03:38,518 --> 00:03:39,785
So I was disappointed.

97
00:03:41,154 --> 00:03:44,289
He was shut down
while he was still totally into her.

98
00:03:45,258 --> 00:03:46,725
- I'll drink soju today.
- Okay.

99
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:48,094
I feel like soju.

100
00:03:48,396 --> 00:03:50,062
- What about food?
- What do you want?

101
00:03:50,964 --> 00:03:51,697
I'll choose...

102
00:03:52,099 --> 00:03:53,132
Should we drop the honorifics?

103
00:03:53,367 --> 00:03:54,567
- Okay.
- I'll choose tofu and kimchi.

104
00:03:54,735 --> 00:03:55,768
Tofu and kimchi.

105
00:03:56,036 --> 00:03:57,903
How did you end up here?

106
00:03:58,639 --> 00:03:59,672
- Sorry?
- Your choice.

107
00:03:59,706 --> 00:04:00,673
- You mean this?
- Yes.

108
00:04:00,674 --> 00:04:01,874
I told them myself.

109
00:04:02,075 --> 00:04:03,342
I told them myself.

110
00:04:03,343 --> 00:04:04,343
- Oh, really?
- Yes.

111
00:04:04,344 --> 00:04:05,277
(Happy)

112
00:04:06,246 --> 00:04:09,248
You and I haven't had
a proper conversation yet.

113
00:04:12,753 --> 00:04:15,555
I was really surprised that this woman,

114
00:04:16,123 --> 00:04:19,258
Ji Hye, was sitting in front of me.

115
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:22,294
Today has been like...

116
00:04:22,763 --> 00:04:25,098
a spectacular roller coaster ride for me.

117
00:04:26,166 --> 00:04:27,767
His heartbreak was healed by Ji Hye.

118
00:04:27,768 --> 00:04:29,235
A new older woman showed up.

119
00:04:29,236 --> 00:04:30,136
(His wounded heart is being healed.)

120
00:04:30,137 --> 00:04:31,537
Actually, I've only talked...

121
00:04:31,538 --> 00:04:34,140
to two people since I got here.

122
00:04:35,442 --> 00:04:36,609
So I was curious.

123
00:04:36,743 --> 00:04:38,844
By the way, I chose you on the first day.
For my first impression.

124
00:04:38,979 --> 00:04:40,012
- Really?
- Yes.

125
00:04:42,049 --> 00:04:43,316
That's very unexpected.

126
00:04:43,317 --> 00:04:44,350
- Really?
- Yes.

127
00:04:45,119 --> 00:04:46,552
The person I wanted to talk to...

128
00:04:47,888 --> 00:04:48,855
was you, Ji Hye.

129
00:04:50,290 --> 00:04:51,156
At first?

130
00:04:52,059 --> 00:04:52,925
It always has been.

131
00:04:53,326 --> 00:04:54,893
Stop lying!

132
00:04:55,195 --> 00:04:57,997
I had two people, Yu Jin and you.

133
00:04:58,131 --> 00:05:00,432
You two were the ones.

134
00:05:00,433 --> 00:05:03,602
I chose Yu Jin
in the First Impression Vote.

135
00:05:03,603 --> 00:05:07,106
After that, I sent the QR to you.

136
00:05:09,042 --> 00:05:11,110
(Clicking)

137
00:05:11,745 --> 00:05:15,648
(Jun Han's Love QR to Ji Hye)

138
00:05:15,649 --> 00:05:16,682
Ji Hye is...

139
00:05:17,350 --> 00:05:19,551
closest to my ideal type appearance-wise.

140
00:05:19,619 --> 00:05:20,986
No way!

141
00:05:21,455 --> 00:05:23,557
Oh, was it you who sent me the QR...

142
00:05:23,558 --> 00:05:25,625
- with the picture of Yeon House?
- Yes.

143
00:05:27,227 --> 00:05:29,762
You've always been someone
I wanted to talk to.

144
00:05:29,763 --> 00:05:31,230
It was a shame that I couldn't.

145
00:05:31,231 --> 00:05:32,598
Oh, really?

146
00:05:33,166 --> 00:05:34,466
(Jun Han's feelings finally
find their way.)

147
00:05:34,467 --> 00:05:35,567
I see.

148
00:05:35,568 --> 00:05:37,469
Every moment makes their hearts flutter.

149
00:05:39,306 --> 00:05:40,573
I kind of showed it in secret.

150
00:05:41,575 --> 00:05:43,342
I'm sorry, but I didn't catch that at all.

151
00:05:43,343 --> 00:05:44,243
You're the same.

152
00:05:44,377 --> 00:05:45,210
- Really?
- Yes.

153
00:05:45,946 --> 00:05:46,846
Really?

154
00:05:48,181 --> 00:05:49,581
I really did want to talk to you.

155
00:05:50,583 --> 00:05:51,317
I agree.

156
00:05:51,618 --> 00:05:53,686
- I'd regret it if I didn't.
- Right.

157
00:05:53,987 --> 00:05:55,120
Let's just follow your heart.

158
00:05:56,323 --> 00:05:57,356
So no regrets now?

159
00:05:58,492 --> 00:06:00,526
- Are you satisfied now?
- I think I am now.

160
00:06:00,660 --> 00:06:01,793
- Really?
- I'm good now.

161
00:06:02,529 --> 00:06:05,664
Actually, there's no one else
I want to get to know better now.

162
00:06:05,665 --> 00:06:06,398
No one?

163
00:06:06,833 --> 00:06:08,367
So are you still interested?

164
00:06:08,368 --> 00:06:09,868
- In whom?
- In Jung Won.

165
00:06:12,906 --> 00:06:14,073
You're very straightforward.

166
00:06:14,674 --> 00:06:15,941
So straightforward.

167
00:06:16,443 --> 00:06:19,412
We're not that close,
but we're talking casually.

168
00:06:19,913 --> 00:06:23,215
It feels like
I'm on a blind date with you.

169
00:06:23,517 --> 00:06:24,684
But with Jung Won...

170
00:06:25,385 --> 00:06:27,619
It feels like I'm with someone
I've known for a long time.

171
00:06:27,788 --> 00:06:29,489
That sounds better for me.

172
00:06:29,490 --> 00:06:31,491
- That's the vibe I got.
- So how is the blind date going?

173
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:33,059
Who knows?

174
00:06:34,361 --> 00:06:37,431
But I think a lot of things
will change for me starting today.

175
00:06:37,432 --> 00:06:40,099
- Really?
- If you keep doing this,

176
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:41,434
you're just giving me dopamine.

177
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:45,303
(Well...)

178
00:06:45,304 --> 00:06:47,539
So it's Jung Won versus me?

179
00:06:48,242 --> 00:06:49,008
Are we competing?

180
00:06:50,043 --> 00:06:50,876
It's a secret.

181
00:06:51,244 --> 00:06:52,711
- I guess I'm right.
- I don't know.

182
00:06:56,917 --> 00:06:57,984
My dopamine has always been you.

183
00:06:58,819 --> 00:06:59,952
My dopamine has always been you.

184
00:07:02,389 --> 00:07:04,423
(Jun Han shows his honest feelings
while they're at it.)

185
00:07:04,424 --> 00:07:05,191
Okay.

186
00:07:06,126 --> 00:07:08,728
- That matters to me.
- That's how I feel anyway.

187
00:07:08,729 --> 00:07:11,697
I think you're blushing.
Your ears turned red.

188
00:07:12,332 --> 00:07:13,265
No, it's just the alcohol.

189
00:07:14,100 --> 00:07:14,966
Just the alcohol.

190
00:07:22,075 --> 00:07:23,709
- I don't know.
- So it's one against three?

191
00:07:25,545 --> 00:07:28,647
You're such an alpha female, aren't you?

192
00:07:29,850 --> 00:07:32,385
You're basically a queen here.

193
00:07:34,321 --> 00:07:35,254
I still got it, right?

194
00:07:35,889 --> 00:07:36,789
I still got it.

195
00:07:39,025 --> 00:07:41,026
I think Ji Hye is...

196
00:07:41,027 --> 00:07:43,061
- kind of enjoying it.
- She likes it.

197
00:07:43,931 --> 00:07:45,631
- It was awkward for her at first.
- She seems comfortable.

198
00:07:45,632 --> 00:07:47,032
Ji Hye is having a good time.

199
00:07:48,068 --> 00:07:49,835
She was cute.

200
00:07:50,637 --> 00:07:53,005
So I loved the date with her.

201
00:07:53,573 --> 00:07:56,375
All the things
that broke my heart before...

202
00:07:56,376 --> 00:07:57,943
were healed by her.

203
00:07:59,446 --> 00:08:02,882
The date with Jun Han...

204
00:08:02,883 --> 00:08:04,583
I really had fun.

205
00:08:05,285 --> 00:08:06,485
It felt like something had begun.

206
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:08,954
Your ears turned red.

207
00:08:09,380 --> 00:08:11,190
(What change will
Jun Han and Ji Hye's date bring?)

208
00:08:11,191 --> 00:08:12,091
Maybe I'm shy.

209
00:08:13,193 --> 00:08:14,059
I think I am.

210
00:08:15,195 --> 00:08:17,530
I think
they'll be okay if they hit it off.

211
00:08:17,531 --> 00:08:20,132
- But the timing is a little off for them.
- Right.

212
00:08:20,934 --> 00:08:23,502
But Jun Han might like that too.

213
00:08:23,503 --> 00:08:25,637
In the end, regardless of anything else,

214
00:08:25,638 --> 00:08:28,274
Ji Hye coming here instead
of going to Jung Won was...

215
00:08:28,275 --> 00:08:30,008
one of the best things
she could have done.

216
00:08:30,009 --> 00:08:31,743
Oh, yes.
If she had been one of those four...

217
00:08:31,744 --> 00:08:33,011
It's better to be his queen...

218
00:08:33,012 --> 00:08:34,746
- than one of many fangirls!
- Right.

219
00:08:35,982 --> 00:08:38,951
(Meanwhile, at Yeon House)

220
00:08:39,119 --> 00:08:42,588
(The two are having a meal.)

221
00:08:43,556 --> 00:08:44,756
Oh, this is...

222
00:08:45,792 --> 00:08:47,244
They're the ones who returned early.

223
00:08:52,365 --> 00:08:53,565
We need to move.

224
00:08:54,801 --> 00:08:58,937
(They didn't receive any request...)

225
00:08:58,938 --> 00:09:06,645
(for an Extended Date or New Date.)

226
00:09:07,514 --> 00:09:09,415
- It's 9:03 p.m.
- Is it nine?

227
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,920
It would be really nice to be on a date...

228
00:09:14,921 --> 00:09:17,156
with someone you like until this hour.

229
00:09:18,058 --> 00:09:19,759
- Isn't it?
- Are you saying that to tease me?

230
00:09:20,026 --> 00:09:20,892
No, me.

231
00:09:22,228 --> 00:09:23,562
- I'm hoping it was me.
- Really?

232
00:09:23,563 --> 00:09:24,629
Really?

233
00:09:25,832 --> 00:09:29,334
(Who does Si Won have in mind?)

234
00:09:29,969 --> 00:09:33,004
(Last night)

235
00:09:33,373 --> 00:09:36,675
(Yu Jin expressed her feelings
to Si Won during "Truth or Dare.")

236
00:09:36,676 --> 00:09:38,744
I told them
that I don't have a second favorite.

237
00:09:40,647 --> 00:09:43,749
(Just remember
that I have feelings for you.)

238
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:48,353
(Ji Seung also showed
Si Won her honest feelings.)

239
00:09:49,089 --> 00:09:53,392
(But neither Yu Jin
nor Ji Seung chose Si Won.)

240
00:09:54,127 --> 00:09:54,927
That's right.

241
00:09:55,595 --> 00:09:56,762
- After that?
- After that...

242
00:09:56,763 --> 00:09:59,498
After she said that,
she extended her date with Jin Woo!

243
00:10:00,133 --> 00:10:01,666
Then what about Si Won?

244
00:10:01,666 --> 00:10:03,733
Well, I don't understand Yu Jin either.

245
00:10:04,433 --> 00:10:06,100
She went to Jung Won.

246
00:10:06,433 --> 00:10:08,733
- That's true.
- What's wrong with everyone?

247
00:10:08,733 --> 00:10:10,200
With the ladies?

248
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,500
I wouldn't be able to trust any woman.

249
00:10:13,466 --> 00:10:14,733
To be honest,

250
00:10:16,066 --> 00:10:19,133
I couldn't sleep
thinking about what to ask her.

251
00:10:20,233 --> 00:10:23,266
I want to ask if she thought of me...

252
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:25,366
when she was on a date with Jun Han.

253
00:10:29,233 --> 00:10:31,533
- When I was on a date,
- You thought about her a lot.

254
00:10:31,533 --> 00:10:33,366
I thought about Ju Hee a lot.

255
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:37,233
He's still talking about Ju Hee.

256
00:10:37,233 --> 00:10:39,000
What do you like about her?

257
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,100
I'm curious now.

258
00:10:42,466 --> 00:10:44,433
I love her smile.

259
00:10:44,433 --> 00:10:47,166
- Her smile?
- Her upper cheek dimples.

260
00:10:47,166 --> 00:10:48,233
Is that so?

261
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:51,000
The best way I can describe her is...

262
00:10:51,819 --> 00:10:55,100
that she looks like a fairy to me.

263
00:10:55,466 --> 00:10:56,500
A fairy?

264
00:10:57,900 --> 00:11:00,633
- I also admire this about her.
- What?

265
00:11:02,066 --> 00:11:05,933
I've been making it clear to everyone
that I'm into her,

266
00:11:06,266 --> 00:11:08,866
but she still chooses other guys...

267
00:11:08,866 --> 00:11:11,333
and tries to get to know them.

268
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:13,800
I think that takes a lot of courage.

269
00:11:13,800 --> 00:11:14,866
Right. It's not easy.

270
00:11:14,866 --> 00:11:16,566
I love that she does what she wants to do.

271
00:11:17,033 --> 00:11:18,233
He can accept all about her.

272
00:11:18,633 --> 00:11:19,700
Of course, it upsets me.

273
00:11:19,700 --> 00:11:20,633
And makes me sad.

274
00:11:20,900 --> 00:11:26,066
But that's a good thing about her
and what's charming about her.

275
00:11:26,733 --> 00:11:29,700
As a younger man, he's just...

276
00:11:30,266 --> 00:11:31,766
delusional.

277
00:11:31,766 --> 00:11:33,300
It's understandable
because he really likes her.

278
00:11:33,300 --> 00:11:34,600
"Delusional" is too harsh.

279
00:11:35,266 --> 00:11:37,133
He'll start to see things.

280
00:11:37,533 --> 00:11:41,266
And by the time he even hears things,
the show will be finished.

281
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:42,500
I'll go in.

282
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:44,000
- See you.
- Bye.

283
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:48,333
(The older woman and younger men
return after their dates.)

284
00:11:49,433 --> 00:11:52,233
(Jung Won comes back
with three older women.)

285
00:11:52,233 --> 00:11:54,300
Jung Won owns the world.

286
00:11:55,266 --> 00:11:57,433
- Come back out as soon as you change.
- Okay.

287
00:11:57,433 --> 00:12:01,300
(They head back to their rooms,
promising to meet up in the common area.)

288
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,500
- Did you have a date?
- Yes. Who did you go out with?

289
00:12:05,233 --> 00:12:07,100
I was with Yun So at first,

290
00:12:07,100 --> 00:12:08,700
and then Jung Won.

291
00:12:09,366 --> 00:12:11,166
- That's good.
- Who did you go out with first?

292
00:12:11,166 --> 00:12:12,133
Jin Woo.

293
00:12:12,466 --> 00:12:13,433
And after that?

294
00:12:13,666 --> 00:12:16,200
I stayed with Jin Woo.

295
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,266
Really?

296
00:12:17,266 --> 00:12:18,933
Everyone finds it surprising.

297
00:12:20,300 --> 00:12:22,300
(Then Ju Hee comes over.)

298
00:12:22,300 --> 00:12:23,533
Hi.

299
00:12:23,833 --> 00:12:25,033
To be honest...

300
00:12:25,866 --> 00:12:29,166
Si Won and I talked a lot in the room,

301
00:12:29,466 --> 00:12:31,866
so I wanted to talk more
with Jin Woo today...

302
00:12:31,866 --> 00:12:33,766
because he spent his day with me.

303
00:12:33,766 --> 00:12:36,033
I thought you'd go out with Si Won.

304
00:12:36,900 --> 00:12:39,533
- Si Won? Right.
- Honestly...

305
00:12:39,533 --> 00:12:42,100
- We think differently every day.
- Right.

306
00:12:42,100 --> 00:12:44,566
I'd been talking to Si Won,

307
00:12:44,566 --> 00:12:46,966
so I thought we'd have
more opportunities to talk.

308
00:12:46,966 --> 00:12:49,766
- You talked yesterday.
- We had a talk yesterday too.

309
00:12:52,900 --> 00:12:54,433
(Why didn't you extend the date
with Si Won?)

310
00:12:54,433 --> 00:12:57,333
I thought after today,

311
00:12:57,833 --> 00:13:00,433
I'd get to talk to Si Won more,

312
00:13:00,433 --> 00:13:01,833
so I didn't bother.

313
00:13:02,666 --> 00:13:03,433
What?

314
00:13:03,433 --> 00:13:06,700
I thought he would understand...

315
00:13:07,233 --> 00:13:09,266
where I stand with him.

316
00:13:09,266 --> 00:13:13,466
He's the one I've talked to the most.

317
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:18,633
Yesterday, she told Si Won
she didn't have a second favorite.

318
00:13:18,633 --> 00:13:20,733
She said he was her only favorite.

319
00:13:21,105 --> 00:13:23,766
But at the extended date,
she chose to be with Jin Woo, not Si Won.

320
00:13:23,766 --> 00:13:26,100
And now, she says
she'll go all-in for Si Won.

321
00:13:26,566 --> 00:13:28,633
She didn't do anything wrong,

322
00:13:28,633 --> 00:13:31,400
but what she did is a bit odd.

323
00:13:32,866 --> 00:13:36,600
So, you don't really want
to get to know Jun Han?

324
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:39,666
So after the overnight date,
your feelings didn't grow.

325
00:13:39,666 --> 00:13:42,133
No. I'm not curious about him anymore.

326
00:13:42,133 --> 00:13:43,100
- Really?
- Yes.

327
00:13:43,100 --> 00:13:45,000
Ju Hee is sure of herself.

328
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,433
Was he different from what you thought?

329
00:13:46,433 --> 00:13:47,433
For example...

330
00:13:47,433 --> 00:13:49,333
We just don't click.

331
00:13:49,333 --> 00:13:51,100
Was it that clear?

332
00:13:51,100 --> 00:13:53,866
I felt like we didn't really click
when we talked.

333
00:13:53,866 --> 00:13:54,733
Really?

334
00:13:55,666 --> 00:13:58,633
He plays around from time to time,

335
00:13:58,633 --> 00:14:00,666
and I don't think I'm into that.

336
00:14:00,666 --> 00:14:02,466
- You're more serious.
- I am.

337
00:14:02,900 --> 00:14:05,666
That's uncomfortable
and a bit overwhelming.

338
00:14:05,666 --> 00:14:08,100
We don't connect emotionally.

339
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:09,966
- Right.
- It's not fun.

340
00:14:11,233 --> 00:14:14,966
After talking to Jun Han,

341
00:14:15,266 --> 00:14:19,466
I realized I like someone
who I can talk to easily.

342
00:14:19,466 --> 00:14:22,733
Yun So and I really get along,

343
00:14:22,733 --> 00:14:25,733
so I was going to talk to him today.

344
00:14:26,433 --> 00:14:27,766
- To Yun So?
- Yes.

345
00:14:27,766 --> 00:14:30,133
I wanted to talk to him.

346
00:14:30,133 --> 00:14:32,600
What do you want to talk about with him?

347
00:14:33,966 --> 00:14:35,000
About the situation now.

348
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:37,566
- The current situation?
- And it's like...

349
00:14:37,566 --> 00:14:39,166
I feel sorry for everything,

350
00:14:39,166 --> 00:14:45,466
but I had to talk to people
I was curious about.

351
00:14:46,466 --> 00:14:48,333
She looked into other options
and came back to Yun So.

352
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:50,133
- For real?
- Yes.

353
00:14:50,133 --> 00:14:53,133
That's why you should get
to know other people too.

354
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:56,533
(Meanwhile, the younger men)

355
00:14:56,900 --> 00:14:57,733
Hey.

356
00:14:58,566 --> 00:14:59,600
Why are you sighing?

357
00:15:02,233 --> 00:15:03,966
Jin Young's first date was...

358
00:15:03,966 --> 00:15:04,900
Me.

359
00:15:04,900 --> 00:15:06,900
- How was it?
- We hit it off.

360
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:08,200
That's why she extended.

361
00:15:08,966 --> 00:15:10,466
Jin Young extended the date,

362
00:15:10,466 --> 00:15:12,400
and the other two chose you
and joined you.

363
00:15:12,400 --> 00:15:13,233
Yes.

364
00:15:13,233 --> 00:15:14,566
How did you feel at the moment?

365
00:15:15,233 --> 00:15:18,333
To be honest, I wanted to talk more
to Jin Young alone.

366
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:20,200
- You guys clicked.
- We couldn't talk that much.

367
00:15:20,500 --> 00:15:23,133
- You guys hit it off.
- I just wanted to talk more.

368
00:15:23,133 --> 00:15:27,300
Jun Han, your first date was Ju Hee today.

369
00:15:27,300 --> 00:15:28,166
Yes.

370
00:15:28,166 --> 00:15:30,433
And she didn't extend our date.

371
00:15:30,433 --> 00:15:33,600
While I was waiting, all of a sudden,

372
00:15:34,033 --> 00:15:35,033
Ji Hye showed up.

373
00:15:35,933 --> 00:15:37,500
They didn't tell you in advance?

374
00:15:37,500 --> 00:15:38,900
You went there, and Ji Hye came?

375
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:42,200
Yes. So I had drinks with Ji Hye.

376
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:44,300
I feel bad for Jin Woo.

377
00:15:44,533 --> 00:15:51,066
I hope you don't take this personally.

378
00:15:51,066 --> 00:15:54,033
- What?
- You only had eyes for Ji Hye.

379
00:15:54,633 --> 00:15:55,466
About what?

380
00:15:55,466 --> 00:15:57,700
That Ji Hye and I drank.

381
00:15:57,700 --> 00:16:01,366
- You did it within the rules.
- It was Ji Hye's choice.

382
00:16:01,366 --> 00:16:02,866
Ji Hye chose you,

383
00:16:02,866 --> 00:16:05,466
went to the spot, and drank with you.

384
00:16:05,466 --> 00:16:06,633
That was within the rules.

385
00:16:06,900 --> 00:16:07,700
I'm not upset at all.

386
00:16:08,433 --> 00:16:10,300
I could end up with Ji Hye.

387
00:16:10,300 --> 00:16:11,800
You could too.

388
00:16:12,233 --> 00:16:14,766
Whatever happens,
let's be happy for each other.

389
00:16:15,533 --> 00:16:17,800
If neither of us ends up with her...

390
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:19,500
Jung Won is popular,

391
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:20,800
but he might end up alone too.

392
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:21,666
That's true.

393
00:16:21,666 --> 00:16:25,733
It's best not to let our emotions
depend on the situation.

394
00:16:25,733 --> 00:16:26,533
Right.

395
00:16:27,233 --> 00:16:31,066
"I'm a bit upset with Ju Hee."

396
00:16:31,066 --> 00:16:32,566
"I talked to Ji Hye today,"

397
00:16:32,566 --> 00:16:35,066
- "and things might go well between us."
- "It went pretty well."

398
00:16:35,066 --> 00:16:36,833
That's what he dropped on Jin Woo.

399
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:39,800
"I might end up with Ji Hye."

400
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:41,566
"You guys should know."

401
00:16:42,166 --> 00:16:43,666
- You didn't extend the date.
- No.

402
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:45,200
When did you come back?

403
00:16:45,466 --> 00:16:48,000
We came back together
because we were with Jung Won.

404
00:16:48,633 --> 00:16:50,266
I hadn't talked to him before.

405
00:16:50,266 --> 00:16:52,866
- Were you over there?
- Jung Won seems like a good person.

406
00:16:52,866 --> 00:16:58,500
Jung Won has owned his own business
for a while,

407
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:01,066
- so he comes across as mature.
- Yes.

408
00:17:01,066 --> 00:17:02,933
Is he the most mature among them?

409
00:17:02,933 --> 00:17:05,366
I talked to Jung Won
for a while yesterday.

410
00:17:05,366 --> 00:17:07,566
Yes. You guys talked for a long time.

411
00:17:07,566 --> 00:17:11,066
Jung Won and I share similar views
on work.

412
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:17,466
Jun Han and I have similar values
when it comes to dating.

413
00:17:17,466 --> 00:17:19,333
So I want to talk to Jun Han more.

414
00:17:19,333 --> 00:17:23,933
I like that Si Won is always the same,

415
00:17:23,933 --> 00:17:26,200
so I want to talk to him too.

416
00:17:27,566 --> 00:17:28,600
It's not easy.

417
00:17:28,600 --> 00:17:33,366
(Ji Seung found out Si Won is one
of the guys Yu Jin is still into.)

418
00:17:36,525 --> 00:17:37,700
We got a message.

419
00:17:37,700 --> 00:17:39,733
(Then they receive a message.)

420
00:17:40,266 --> 00:17:42,233
(Please come to the front
of the QR Room and take a seat.)

421
00:17:42,233 --> 00:17:44,133
What are they going to do?

422
00:17:44,133 --> 00:17:45,866
"Please come to the front
of the QR Room..."

423
00:17:45,866 --> 00:17:47,666
"and take a seat."

424
00:17:47,666 --> 00:17:48,666
To the front of the QR Room?

425
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:51,400
Shouldn't you hurry up...

426
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,333
to sit next to Ju Hee?

427
00:17:53,333 --> 00:17:54,266
I should.

428
00:17:55,233 --> 00:17:56,733
(Where the older women
and younger men gather)

429
00:17:56,733 --> 00:17:58,100
What's going on here?

430
00:17:58,366 --> 00:17:59,700
- What's this?
- What is that?

431
00:17:59,700 --> 00:18:00,766
No way.

432
00:18:01,100 --> 00:18:02,400
Wait.

433
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:04,166
- Is it...
- That!

434
00:18:04,166 --> 00:18:05,600
I know what this is.

435
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:06,800
Did you watch Season One?

436
00:18:07,366 --> 00:18:08,800
(Ten seats on the grass)

437
00:18:08,800 --> 00:18:09,800
Will they reveal their age?

438
00:18:11,166 --> 00:18:13,033
Age reveal?

439
00:18:13,033 --> 00:18:16,300
- Those bean bags meant their age.
- Is that so?

440
00:18:16,300 --> 00:18:17,833
Please tell us how old they are.

441
00:18:18,100 --> 00:18:21,633
(Ji Hye leaves the seats
on both sides empty.)

442
00:18:21,633 --> 00:18:22,733
Why am I nervous?

443
00:18:22,733 --> 00:18:23,533
Why?

444
00:18:24,100 --> 00:18:26,150
My heart pounds
every time we do something.

445
00:18:26,151 --> 00:18:28,066
Why is your heart pounding?

446
00:18:28,600 --> 00:18:29,833
(Glancing over)

447
00:18:30,233 --> 00:18:31,400
Don't get nervous.

448
00:18:31,400 --> 00:18:32,766
- Is there a hand warmer too?
- Yes.

449
00:18:32,766 --> 00:18:33,800
(Ji Seung goes next to Si Won.)

450
00:18:34,962 --> 00:18:36,200
What did you do on the date?

451
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:39,600
We made keychains.

452
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:41,733
Keychains? That sounds fun.

453
00:18:41,733 --> 00:18:44,500
Ju Hee used to cover her face like this,

454
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:45,533
saying she was cold.

455
00:18:45,533 --> 00:18:48,500
The old Ju Hee would do that
to block her view.

456
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:51,166
- She's pulled it back.
- Now she just relaxes.

457
00:18:51,166 --> 00:18:52,366
(Ju Hee's attitude has changed.)

458
00:18:52,366 --> 00:18:53,400
What did you have for dinner?

459
00:18:53,866 --> 00:18:57,000
- We had Korean beef tartare.
- Korean beef?

460
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:58,133
Korean beef tartare?

461
00:18:58,466 --> 00:19:00,800
You had a delicious dinner
if you had Korean beef tartare.

462
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:02,100
Let me tell you this.

463
00:19:02,100 --> 00:19:04,566
We took the cable car,

464
00:19:04,566 --> 00:19:08,300
and he and I were talking at the top.

465
00:19:08,900 --> 00:19:12,666
Then I received a text
asking if I wanted to extend it.

466
00:19:12,666 --> 00:19:16,233
- And I thought I wanted to eat at least.
- That's why?

467
00:19:16,233 --> 00:19:18,700
So I said yes, and we went to a wine bar.

468
00:19:18,966 --> 00:19:20,166
That was a good date.

469
00:19:20,166 --> 00:19:23,400
But we stayed longer than we thought.

470
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,333
At the wine bar?

471
00:19:25,166 --> 00:19:29,933
(Ji Seung explains
why she extended her date with Jin Woo.)

472
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:34,333
(It's hard to read Si Won's face.)

473
00:19:34,666 --> 00:19:38,100
She's saying she extended it
with a good intention...

474
00:19:38,100 --> 00:19:40,133
and it didn't mean anything.

475
00:19:40,666 --> 00:19:43,366
- Would it feel that way to him?
- I know.

476
00:19:43,366 --> 00:19:45,633
Or would it sound like an excuse?

477
00:19:45,633 --> 00:19:47,066
I don't know what he thinks about it.

478
00:19:47,600 --> 00:19:49,633
(Jung Won didn't sit next to Ji Hye.)

479
00:19:50,033 --> 00:19:50,866
Sit here.

480
00:19:50,866 --> 00:19:51,566
(Tapping)

481
00:19:51,966 --> 00:19:54,400
(Jung Won has Jin Young sit next to him.)

482
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:56,666
- I need to wake up.
- What?

483
00:19:56,666 --> 00:19:58,519
I'm feeling too tired.

484
00:19:58,875 --> 00:20:00,336
I should get myself together.

485
00:20:00,433 --> 00:20:02,200
It feels better that I'm now outside.

486
00:20:03,102 --> 00:20:07,105
(All the older women
and the young men have gathered.)

487
00:20:07,506 --> 00:20:08,873
What could it be?

488
00:20:09,342 --> 00:20:10,208
I'm curious.

489
00:20:11,811 --> 00:20:12,863
Could it be our age reveal?

490
00:20:13,913 --> 00:20:16,181
I'm so clueless. What would it be?

491
00:20:16,849 --> 00:20:19,317
I don't want to check it out.

492
00:20:20,319 --> 00:20:21,710
- I really don't.
- We'll spend the remaining...

493
00:20:21,711 --> 00:20:23,221
three days, knowing each other's age.

494
00:20:23,222 --> 00:20:25,790
(The older women get nervous
as it could be an age reveal.)

495
00:20:26,158 --> 00:20:31,262
(And the younger men are curious
about the ladies' age.)

496
00:20:31,831 --> 00:20:34,633
There's a screen,
so we'll be watching something.

497
00:20:35,501 --> 00:20:36,568
It's on.

498
00:20:37,269 --> 00:20:39,103
- What?
- No way.

499
00:20:40,006 --> 00:20:41,106
I'm so curious too.

500
00:20:41,641 --> 00:20:42,774
It must be their age.

501
00:20:42,775 --> 00:20:44,643
- The bean bag meant the age.
- I'm certain.

502
00:20:45,645 --> 00:20:50,449
(Chapter 1, Our childhood)

503
00:20:50,450 --> 00:20:52,551
The generation gap between them
will be pretty obvious.

504
00:20:53,919 --> 00:20:55,720
- Gosh.
- Unbelievable.

505
00:20:57,923 --> 00:20:59,690
(Surprised)

506
00:20:59,691 --> 00:21:00,825
So cute!

507
00:21:02,361 --> 00:21:05,540
(Ji Seung at three,
with irresistibly chubby cheeks)

508
00:21:05,564 --> 00:21:06,931
- She's making a heart.
- She's so adorable.

509
00:21:08,367 --> 00:21:09,167
(Shy)

510
00:21:09,168 --> 00:21:10,368
She looks super cute.

511
00:21:11,370 --> 00:21:13,304
I was really startled.

512
00:21:13,305 --> 00:21:14,172
(Smiling)

513
00:21:15,041 --> 00:21:16,008
It's me.

514
00:21:19,478 --> 00:21:20,144
Gosh.

515
00:21:20,145 --> 00:21:21,879
She's probably around my age.

516
00:21:22,682 --> 00:21:23,816
Oh, my!

517
00:21:25,217 --> 00:21:26,984
She had a beautiful smile even back then.

518
00:21:28,287 --> 00:21:29,087
Oh, my!

519
00:21:30,923 --> 00:21:32,023
(Glancing)

520
00:21:34,393 --> 00:21:35,460
(Ji Hye striking a confident pose at five)

521
