than Jung Won and Jin Woo.)

777
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:03,966
Born in 1992?

778
00:32:04,466 --> 00:32:05,965
You look so much younger than that.

779
00:32:05,966 --> 00:32:08,132
(And she's eight years older
than Jun Han.)

780
00:32:08,133 --> 00:32:09,594
Yes, I'm 35.

781
00:32:11,466 --> 00:32:12,697
I do look on the younger side.

782
00:32:15,866 --> 00:32:16,699
How old are you?

783
00:32:16,700 --> 00:32:18,365
(Next up is Jin Young.)

784
00:32:18,366 --> 00:32:18,993
Me?

785
00:32:19,017 --> 00:32:20,900
I'm so curious about her age too.

786
00:32:25,533 --> 00:32:27,666
I'm guessing you were born in 1994.

787
00:32:27,966 --> 00:32:29,965
Maybe 1994 or 1995?

788
00:32:29,966 --> 00:32:31,733
(Everyone has a different guess
for Jin Young.)

789
00:32:31,941 --> 00:32:32,974
I was...

790
00:32:33,666 --> 00:32:35,033
born in 1997,

791
00:32:37,266 --> 00:32:38,865
so I'm 30.

792
00:32:38,866 --> 00:32:40,500
(Jin Young, 30)

793
00:32:40,633 --> 00:32:42,900
Wait, she's 30?

794
00:32:44,300 --> 00:32:45,332
Hold on!

795
00:32:45,333 --> 00:32:46,565
You were born in 1997?

796
00:32:46,566 --> 00:32:49,000
Then I'm only a year older than you.

797
00:32:49,533 --> 00:32:50,466
She's a baby!

798
00:32:55,933 --> 00:32:56,865
What?

799
00:32:56,866 --> 00:32:58,365
Anyway...

800
00:32:58,366 --> 00:32:59,833
(She's only a year older
than Jin Woo and Jung Won.)

801
00:33:00,200 --> 00:33:02,632
A one-year gap doesn't even count
as being older.

802
00:33:02,633 --> 00:33:04,032
Yeah, that's barely a difference.

803
00:33:04,033 --> 00:33:05,932
She's not an older woman.
She's just a woman.

804
00:33:05,933 --> 00:33:06,932
A single year means nothing.

805
00:33:06,933 --> 00:33:09,099
Jung Won must be thrilled.

806
00:33:09,100 --> 00:33:10,899
Finding out she's only a year older...

807
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:12,365
will probably make him like her even more.

808
00:33:12,366 --> 00:33:16,032
A year apart basically means
they're the same age.

809
00:33:16,033 --> 00:33:17,865
That's a total win-win for both of them.

810
00:33:17,866 --> 00:33:23,099
I never expected the age gap
to be this small.

811
00:33:23,100 --> 00:33:26,033
This could completely change the dynamics.

812
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:28,799
I really want to know Ji Seung's age now.

813
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:31,833
How old do you think Ji Seung is?

814
00:33:33,033 --> 00:33:34,399
(Staring)

815
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:36,432
Ji Seung? I'm thinking 33.

816
00:33:36,433 --> 00:33:37,233
Born in 1993?

817
00:33:38,333 --> 00:33:40,099
She has this calm vibe
that makes her seem...

818
00:33:40,100 --> 00:33:42,933
like she's maybe 34 or 35.

819
00:33:43,493 --> 00:33:44,816
- How old are you?
- Is it 1994?

820
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:45,866
No, 1993.

821
00:33:46,500 --> 00:33:49,099
I was born in 1992.

822
00:33:49,100 --> 00:33:51,400
- We're the same age!
- So I'm 35.

823
00:33:52,666 --> 00:33:55,232
(Ji Seung is ten years older than Si Won.)

824
00:33:55,233 --> 00:33:57,732
She's ten years older than Si Won!

825
00:33:57,733 --> 00:33:59,566
(Peeking)

826
00:34:00,600 --> 00:34:02,065
He looks deep in thought.

827
00:34:02,066 --> 00:34:04,632
I figured she'd be
about eight years older.

828
00:34:04,633 --> 00:34:08,346
But seeing the gap hit double digits
feels a bit different.

829
00:34:08,433 --> 00:34:10,399
Still, that's just a number in my head.

830
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:13,600
If I just think of her as two years older,
I'll be fine.

831
00:34:14,333 --> 00:34:16,800
So it wasn't a total shock.

832
00:34:17,433 --> 00:34:19,599
- What does he mean by "two years older"?
- What kind of math is that?

833
00:34:19,600 --> 00:34:21,265
Where did that logic come from?

834
00:34:21,266 --> 00:34:22,832
Is he treating an eight-year gap as zero?

835
00:34:22,833 --> 00:34:25,366
Seriously? That's hilarious.

836
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:29,699
But I can't just ignore reality.

837
00:34:29,700 --> 00:34:34,232
We're in completely
different chapters of our lives.

838
00:34:34,233 --> 00:34:36,766
So of course it weighed on me.

839
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:41,632
(The two have very different perspectives
on the age gap.)

840
00:34:41,633 --> 00:34:45,365
I guess it's fine for the younger guys,

841
00:34:45,366 --> 00:34:47,599
but the women have to think
about what's next.

842
00:34:47,600 --> 00:34:48,699
You know, marriage and the future.

843
00:34:48,700 --> 00:34:49,599
They don't necessarily have to.

844
00:34:49,600 --> 00:34:53,332
They can just move in together
if she's financially set.

845
00:34:53,333 --> 00:34:54,765
But doesn't Ji Seung have to consider...

846
00:34:54,766 --> 00:34:58,299
whether she can actually support him
in the real world?

847
00:34:58,300 --> 00:34:59,432
Of course she can.

848
00:34:59,433 --> 00:35:01,065
- Really?
- Why not?

849
00:35:01,066 --> 00:35:03,999
You just add one more set of chopsticks
to the table. That's it.

850
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:05,065
What else do you need?

851
00:35:05,066 --> 00:35:06,705
So when's the wedding date?

852
00:35:08,266 --> 00:35:09,633
I'm genuinely curious.

853
00:35:10,300 --> 00:35:12,000
- I have no idea.
- Fair enough.

854
00:35:12,866 --> 00:35:14,400
I really don't know.

855
00:35:15,033 --> 00:35:16,232
I honestly have no clue.

856
00:35:16,233 --> 00:35:17,633
(Now it's time for Ju Hee
to reveal her age.)

857
00:35:17,766 --> 00:35:18,566
Ju Hee.

858
00:35:21,100 --> 00:35:22,065
- Born in 1996, maybe?
- Are you 33?

859
00:35:22,066 --> 00:35:23,332
I'm thinking 1995.

860
00:35:23,333 --> 00:35:26,933
- Maybe 1996, so right around 30?
- Somewhere between 1994 and 1997.

861
00:35:28,033 --> 00:35:30,566
(Nodding)

862
00:35:31,133 --> 00:35:32,297
You weren't born in the '90s?

863
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:33,365
What?

864
00:35:33,366 --> 00:35:34,633
No way! Seriously?

865
00:35:35,030 --> 00:35:37,166
It'd be crazy if you turned out
to be the oldest.

866
00:35:37,700 --> 00:35:39,399
No way, look at her smiling.

867
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:41,432
- You were born in 1993, right?
- Is it 1993?

868
00:35:41,433 --> 00:35:43,665
I was born in 1992.

869
00:35:43,666 --> 00:35:45,432
(Ju Hee, 35)

870
00:35:45,433 --> 00:35:47,000
We're the same age!

871
00:35:47,733 --> 00:35:48,665
(Ju Hee is 10 years older than Yun So.)

872
00:35:48,666 --> 00:35:50,199
They're all the same age.

873
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:52,399
Yun So looks totally blank.
Look at his face.

874
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:53,700
(Tilting his head)

875
00:35:53,933 --> 00:35:56,099
- Yun So!
- He's staring into space.

876
00:35:56,100 --> 00:35:57,365
He's running the numbers.

877
00:35:57,366 --> 00:35:58,299
He's doing the math.

878
00:35:58,300 --> 00:35:59,699
Is he calculating?

879
00:35:59,700 --> 00:36:02,066
Or did his brain just short-circuit?

880
00:36:02,433 --> 00:36:03,232
Yun So's expression is like...

881
00:36:03,233 --> 00:36:04,233
(Reenacting)

882
00:36:09,233 --> 00:36:10,402
"So she's 35."

883
00:36:11,866 --> 00:36:16,133
(What do the two think
about their 11-year age gap?)

884
00:36:16,333 --> 00:36:17,332
We only have one person left.

885
00:36:17,333 --> 00:36:19,066
(Lastly, Yu Jin is
about to reveal her age.)

886
00:36:19,966 --> 00:36:21,065
Let's guess her age.

887
00:36:21,066 --> 00:36:23,100
(How old is Yu Jin, who seemed
the most shaken by the men's ages?)

888
00:36:23,600 --> 00:36:26,466
(Curious)

889
00:36:27,266 --> 00:36:28,575
I'm guessing she was born in 1992.

890
00:36:28,600 --> 00:36:30,099
I think they're all the exact same age.

891
00:36:30,100 --> 00:36:32,033
I'm leaning toward 1992 too.

892
00:36:33,486 --> 00:36:34,779
Maybe 1991?

893
00:36:35,733 --> 00:36:37,308
You give off major eldest-daughter vibes.

894
00:36:37,333 --> 00:36:38,730
Total eldest-daughter energy.

895
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:40,533
- Were you born in 1990?
- Is it 1990?

896
00:36:41,166 --> 00:36:42,099
Yes.

897
00:36:42,100 --> 00:36:43,333
How old?

898
00:36:43,566 --> 00:36:44,900
I was born in 1990.

899
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,032
She's the oldest.

900
00:36:47,033 --> 00:36:49,333
Wait, so you're 25?

901
00:36:50,633 --> 00:36:51,743
Thirty-seven?

902
00:36:53,633 --> 00:36:54,799
Oh, come on!

903
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:55,932
(Seriously, Si Won?)

904
00:36:55,933 --> 00:36:58,866
How can he make a face like that
after hearing her age?

905
00:36:59,666 --> 00:37:02,765
How could he?
She was so shy about revealing it!

906
00:37:02,766 --> 00:37:04,132
- Well, maybe...
- His expression was priceless.

907
00:37:04,133 --> 00:37:06,233
By Si Won's logic,

908
00:37:06,733 --> 00:37:08,133
she's only four years older than him.

909
00:37:09,100 --> 00:37:11,362
Because an eight-year gap
counts as zero to him.

910
00:37:11,500 --> 00:37:14,433
So he probably thinks
four years older is perfect.

911
00:37:14,732 --> 00:37:16,999
I'm so shocked. Wait, you're 25?

912
00:37:19,366 --> 00:37:20,666
Wow, really?

913
00:37:21,433 --> 00:37:22,774
They're all just so young.

914
00:37:26,866 --> 00:37:27,732
What are they going to do?

915
00:37:27,733 --> 00:37:29,833
(Si Won seems completely lost in thought.)

916
00:37:32,800 --> 00:37:34,833
Man. Am I even allowed to be here?

917
00:37:35,300 --> 00:37:36,366
Oh, no.

918
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:42,232
I didn't expect the age gap
to be this massive.

919
00:37:42,233 --> 00:37:43,832
She was thinking
the exact same thing we were.

920
00:37:43,856 --> 00:37:44,366
Yes.

921
00:37:44,866 --> 00:37:47,432
Yu Jin was really into Si Won,

922
00:37:47,433 --> 00:37:49,632
but she just found out
he's 12 years younger than her.

923
00:37:49,633 --> 00:37:52,270
Who do you think is finding it harder?

924
00:37:52,866 --> 00:37:53,666
Both of them?

925
00:37:54,100 --> 00:37:55,432
- Maybe both.
- Will this cause a change of heart?

926
00:37:55,433 --> 00:37:58,433
I think Si Won might be the one
to hesitate more.

927
00:37:59,833 --> 00:38:04,732
Because all the other guys are CEOs,
have their own brands,

928
00:38:04,733 --> 00:38:06,132
or run companies.

929
00:38:06,133 --> 00:38:08,665
They all seem so established.

930
00:38:08,666 --> 00:38:10,710
Meanwhile,
his professional athletic career was...

931
00:38:10,734 --> 00:38:12,132
cut short by an injury.

932
00:38:12,133 --> 00:38:13,632
Sure, he's working now,

933
00:38:13,633 --> 00:38:17,799
but I got the feeling
he feels a bit intimidated.

934
00:38:17,800 --> 00:38:23,165
Especially since the women are all running
their own successful businesses too.

935
00:38:23,166 --> 00:38:24,732
Regardless of everything else,

936
00:38:24,733 --> 00:38:26,766
I think that might be weighing
on Si Won's mind.

937
00:38:27,466 --> 00:38:28,365
Do you think so?

938
00:38:28,366 --> 00:38:30,566
- This is getting interesting.
- I'm so hooked.

939
00:38:31,300 --> 00:38:36,033
(After the age reveal,
everyone gathers back in the living room.)

940
00:38:37,133 --> 00:38:39,000
Si Won, were you born
in the Year of the Horse?

941
00:38:39,276 --> 00:38:40,908
Yeah, I was. You too?

942
00:38:40,933 --> 00:38:42,032
Yes.

943
00:38:42,057 --> 00:38:43,278
What do I even do?

944
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:45,690
So we're a full cycle apart.

945
00:38:49,533 --> 00:38:51,129
Oh no, she's covering her mouth.

946
00:38:51,933 --> 00:38:55,499
I feel like there's no point in me
even being here anymore.

947
00:38:55,500 --> 00:38:56,866
What do you mean by that?

948
00:38:58,366 --> 00:39:00,265
She's completely losing her confidence.

949
00:39:00,266 --> 00:39:02,233
That's not true at all.

950
00:39:03,166 --> 00:39:04,166
Are you okay, Yu Jin?

951
00:39:06,966 --> 00:39:09,165
Yu Jin, you look completely drained.

952
00:39:09,166 --> 00:39:10,000
Do I?

953
00:39:10,300 --> 00:39:12,617
Is it that overwhelming
to find out you're 12 years older?

954
00:39:15,433 --> 00:39:17,163
A million thoughts rushed through my mind.

955
00:39:17,188 --> 00:39:21,533
I had no idea I'd be that much older
than everyone.

956
00:39:22,733 --> 00:39:26,299
Finding out someone's age
when things are already established...

957
00:39:26,300 --> 00:39:29,099
versus finding out when you're still
just getting curious about them,

958
00:39:29,100 --> 00:39:31,832
it feels completely different.

959
00:39:31,833 --> 00:39:33,500
That's understandable.

960
00:39:34,300 --> 00:39:37,665
She really needs to stay confident
right now.

961
00:39:37,666 --> 00:39:39,932
Even though they came onto the show
knowing they'd be older than the guys,

962
00:39:39,933 --> 00:39:42,499
finding out you're
the absolute oldest person there...

963
00:39:42,500 --> 00:39:44,165
can be a really tough pill to swallow.

964
00:39:44,166 --> 00:39:45,966
I totally feel for Yu Jin.

965
00:39:49,833 --> 00:39:51,800
- Let's do a toast.
- Let's do it.

966
00:39:55,133 --> 00:39:56,633
(Sighing)

967
00:39:59,931 --> 00:40:02,432
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

968
00:40:02,433 --> 00:40:03,233
Let's drink.

969
00:40:04,035 --> 00:40:05,703
Yu Jin is sitting so far away from them.

970
00:40:06,571 --> 00:40:07,304
Cheers.

971
00:40:08,072 --> 00:40:08,838
That was great.

972
00:40:10,041 --> 00:40:11,941
What? Do you feel bad for me?

973
00:40:11,942 --> 00:40:13,944
- No, it's just that you didn't toast.
- I did!

974
00:40:13,945 --> 00:40:15,212
(Si Won is looking after Yu Jin.)

975
00:40:15,213 --> 00:40:17,414
Si Won keeps looking out for her.

976
00:40:18,349 --> 00:40:19,783
(Glancing)

977
00:40:21,486 --> 00:40:24,288
We just found out everyone's age.

978
00:40:24,289 --> 00:40:26,390
We basically know everything
about each other now...

979
00:40:26,415 --> 00:40:27,982
halfway through the trip.

980
00:40:28,226 --> 00:40:29,393
(Nodding)

981
00:40:29,394 --> 00:40:30,360
Are you shocked?

982
00:40:30,929 --> 00:40:34,298
Now that I know everyone's age...

983
00:40:34,566 --> 00:40:36,100
Do you feel even better about things?

984
00:40:36,501 --> 00:40:39,036
Everyone is so much younger
than I thought.

985
00:40:39,905 --> 00:40:41,639
- Exactly.
- They really are young.

986
00:40:42,340 --> 00:40:44,508
It was actually better than I expected.

987
00:40:46,110 --> 00:40:47,644
They're way younger than I thought.

988
00:40:47,645 --> 00:40:49,446
Does age really matter?

989
00:40:49,981 --> 00:40:52,049
- It depends on the person.
- Everyone's different.

990
00:40:52,050 --> 00:40:53,784
Everyone has their own standard.

991
00:40:54,152 --> 00:40:55,453
It's not like it doesn't matter.

992
00:40:57,056 --> 00:41:01,358
Even if someone's ten years older,
it doesn't shock me.

993
00:41:02,861 --> 00:41:04,962
(Some feel relieved
after the age reveal...)

994
00:41:04,963 --> 00:41:09,767
(while others have a lot on their minds.)

995
00:41:10,168 --> 00:41:12,302
Did anyone's feelings change?

996
00:41:12,604 --> 00:41:14,471
- Not mine.
- Not at all?

997
00:41:14,906 --> 00:41:16,774
Honestly, nothing really changed for me.

998
00:41:17,909 --> 00:41:19,910
I feel like Yu Jin's feelings
shifted the most.

999
00:41:20,075 --> 00:41:21,654
- Totally.
- It's written all over her face.

1000
00:41:21,679 --> 00:41:23,347
- She seems worried.
- She's gotten so quiet.

1001
00:41:23,348 --> 00:41:24,248
(Yu Jin is quiet.)

1002
00:41:24,350 --> 00:41:25,915
Maybe she's just tired.

1003
00:41:25,916 --> 00:41:27,184
No, I'm not tired.

1004
00:41:27,986 --> 00:41:29,486
Oh, no.

1005
00:41:29,621 --> 00:41:30,887
Are you feeling anxious then?

1006
00:41:30,888 --> 00:41:32,156
- Yeah, I'm really anxious.
- Really?

1007
00:41:32,157 --> 00:41:33,490
Yes, seriously.

1008
00:41:33,491 --> 00:41:35,192
- Really?
- I'm super anxious.

1009
00:41:35,960 --> 00:41:38,396
Is the guy you have in mind
way younger than you expected?

1010
00:41:38,796 --> 00:41:40,330
(Sighing)

1011
00:41:40,598 --> 00:41:42,899
(Yu Jin sighs instead of answering.)

1012
00:41:45,237 --> 00:41:46,037
That must be it.

1013
00:41:46,038 --> 00:41:47,371
What else could it be?

1014
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:51,275
If a guy is much younger,

1015
00:41:51,376 --> 00:41:53,010
does that usually bother a woman?

1016
00:41:53,011 --> 00:41:54,411
What exactly is worrying her?

1017
00:41:54,646 --> 00:41:56,280
Well, it's like this.

1018
00:41:57,616 --> 00:42:00,051
If you've never dated someone that young,

1019
00:42:00,084 --> 00:42:01,586
it makes you a bit worried.

1020
00:42:02,253 --> 00:42:03,221
"Will this be okay?"

1021
00:42:03,588 --> 00:42:05,322
"What if we start dating..."

1022
00:42:05,323 --> 00:42:07,725
"and I just see him as too young for me?"

1023
00:42:09,327 --> 00:42:12,763
You can't help but think about the future.

1024
00:42:12,764 --> 00:42:16,900
(The older women must consider
life after leaving Yeon House.)

1025
00:42:17,669 --> 00:42:20,137
Now that we know everyone's jobs and ages,

1026
00:42:20,138 --> 00:42:21,005
the real game begins.

1027
00:42:21,006 --> 00:42:22,306
It all starts now.

1028
00:42:22,407 --> 00:42:25,843
(How will their feelings shift
after the age reveal?)

1029
00:42:25,844 --> 00:42:28,379
At the beginning of filming,

1030
00:42:28,380 --> 00:42:30,981
I said age wouldn't change anything.

1031
00:42:31,182 --> 00:42:32,315
I take that back now.

1032
00:42:32,750 --> 00:42:34,117
The guys...

1033
00:42:34,319 --> 00:42:36,621
are way younger than I thought.

1034
00:42:36,622 --> 00:42:38,522
So much younger than I ever expected.

1035
00:42:38,523 --> 00:42:41,392
In particular, Yun So is
11 years younger than Ju Hee.

1036
00:42:41,393 --> 00:42:44,061
And he's only had eyes for her.

1037
00:42:44,062 --> 00:42:45,029
But...

1038
00:42:45,530 --> 00:42:48,298
I don't think it'll bother
Yun So that much.

1039
00:42:48,299 --> 00:42:49,062
You think so?

1040
00:42:49,087 --> 00:42:51,969
It might give Ju Hee a lot to think about,

1041
00:42:51,970 --> 00:42:54,204
but Yun So won't care.

1042
00:42:54,205 --> 00:42:56,773
"Ju Hee, I'll take care of you."

1043
00:42:56,975 --> 00:42:59,377
It's the older women
who'll be overthinking.

1044
00:42:59,378 --> 00:43:02,813
Jung Won might become more popular now.

1045
00:43:03,014 --> 00:43:06,116
And since Jin Woo isn't
as young as they thought,

1046
00:43:06,517 --> 00:43:07,884
they might want to approach him.

1047
00:43:07,885 --> 00:43:08,885
(Jung Won and Jin Woo might see
a surge in popularity.)

1048
00:43:09,520 --> 00:43:11,255
(Glancing)

1049
00:43:11,256 --> 00:43:12,523
He's reading her expression.

1050
00:43:13,224 --> 00:43:15,025
(Hesitating)

1051
00:43:15,026 --> 00:43:16,760
Yun So, go talk to her.

1052
00:43:17,028 --> 00:43:19,262
You need to make a move.

1053
00:43:19,263 --> 00:43:20,263
(Glancing over)

1054
00:43:27,538 --> 00:43:29,472
He's walking over.

1055
00:43:30,908 --> 00:43:32,743
- Let's go chat real quick.
- Sounds good.

1056
00:43:33,678 --> 00:43:35,746
- Should we bring this?
- Yeah, let's grab it.

1057
00:43:35,747 --> 00:43:37,214
(After hesitating, Yun So finally
asks Ju Hee to talk.)

1058
00:43:37,215 --> 00:43:38,149
Nice job.

1059
00:43:41,452 --> 00:43:42,786
I feel like I haven't seen you in forever.

1060
00:43:42,787 --> 00:43:44,288
- Tell me about it.
- You're so hard to catch.

1061
00:43:44,389 --> 00:43:46,657
- I know.
- You kept disappearing somewhere.

1062
00:43:46,658 --> 00:43:47,792
Who, me?

1063
00:43:47,793 --> 00:43:48,593
Me?

1064
00:43:48,594 --> 00:43:49,827
You kept slipping away.

1065
00:43:50,194 --> 00:43:51,896
It's so tough to even see your face.

1066
00:43:52,030 --> 00:43:52,931
I know.

1067
00:43:53,365 --> 00:43:55,932
I wanted my first time using
the Talk Room to be with you.

1068
00:43:56,234 --> 00:43:58,769
Well, now's your chance.

1069
00:43:59,971 --> 00:44:01,738
Doesn't Ju Hee...

1070
00:44:01,739 --> 00:44:03,172
- seem completely different?
- She really does.

1071
00:44:03,173 --> 00:44:04,240
She's different.

1072
00:44:04,241 --> 00:44:05,743
She's totally different from yesterday.

1073
00:44:08,646 --> 00:44:10,180
How was your date?

1074
00:44:11,049 --> 00:44:12,282
I want to hear all about it.

1075
00:44:12,283 --> 00:44:13,851
- My date?
- Yeah, yours.

1076
00:44:14,619 --> 00:44:16,219
I'm curious to hear your side.

1077
00:44:16,687 --> 00:44:17,554
- Are you?
- Yeah.

1078
00:44:17,555 --> 00:44:19,489
I can go first, but...

1079
00:44:19,490 --> 00:44:20,923
Do I have to go first?

1080
00:44:20,924 --> 00:44:21,724
You don't have to.

1081
00:44:21,859 --> 00:44:23,661
But I do have a question for you.

1082
00:44:24,095 --> 00:44:24,895
Go ahead.

1083
00:44:26,565 --> 00:44:28,599
Yesterday and the day before,

1084
00:44:29,967 --> 00:44:31,469
when you were out on dates,

1085
00:44:32,003 --> 00:44:33,538
did you think about me at all?

1086
00:44:34,872 --> 00:44:39,375
(Did you think about me?)

1087
00:44:39,376 --> 00:44:40,176
I did.

1088
00:44:41,946 --> 00:44:43,046
- Really?
- Yes.

1089
00:44:43,781 --> 00:44:45,449
This is no joke.

1090
00:44:47,518 --> 00:44:48,284
I honestly...

1091
00:44:50,788 --> 00:44:53,656
felt like I never crossed your mind.

1092
00:44:55,026 --> 00:44:57,160
I felt so down yesterday.

1093
00:44:57,262 --> 00:44:58,896
I wasn't even that upset before that.

1094
00:45:01,866 --> 00:45:04,009
(Your request for an overnight date
was rejected.)

1095
00:45:04,033 --> 00:45:05,235
(Please choose someone else.)

1096
00:45:05,736 --> 00:45:09,172
(Ju Hee's rejection last night...)

1097
00:45:09,173 --> 00:45:12,809
(hit Yun So hard.)

1098
00:45:13,344 --> 00:45:15,345
I mentioned I wanted to talk to Jun Han.

1099
00:45:15,346 --> 00:45:16,346
Right.

1100
00:45:16,647 --> 00:45:18,848
And it felt like...

1101
00:45:20,284 --> 00:45:22,419
you weren't giving me
the space to do that.

1102
00:45:22,420 --> 00:45:24,787
That's why it got to me so much.

1103
00:45:25,556 --> 00:45:27,057
From where I stood,

1104
00:45:27,058 --> 00:45:29,359
I was making my interest in you
pretty obvious,

1105
00:45:29,727 --> 00:45:32,762
but you kept choosing him
for the Love QRs and games.

1106
00:45:32,964 --> 00:45:35,065
It made me feel so anxious.

1107
00:45:35,466 --> 00:45:36,699
It really threw me off.

1108
00:45:36,700 --> 00:45:39,335
I just wanted to spend a day
getting to know him...

1109
00:45:39,336 --> 00:45:41,337
to figure out where I stood.

1110
00:45:41,672 --> 00:45:43,172
Anyway, I did get to talk to him.

1111
00:45:43,173 --> 00:45:44,273
(Ju Hee wanted to get to know Jun Han.)

1112
00:45:44,274 --> 00:45:47,543
But I felt like we didn't really click.

1113
00:45:47,544 --> 00:45:49,046
- That was my takeaway.
- Oh, really?

1114
00:45:49,047 --> 00:45:52,482
I just realized, "So, this is who he is."

1115
00:45:52,483 --> 00:45:55,551
And today, I wanted to focus on talking...

1116
00:45:56,854 --> 00:45:59,055
to people I hadn't really
chatted with yet.

1117
00:45:59,056 --> 00:46:00,490
(Which is why Ju Hee chose Jung Won today)

1118
00:46:01,059 --> 00:46:01,925
So...

1119
00:46:02,360 --> 00:46:04,361
(Hesitating)

1120
00:46:04,996 --> 00:46:07,030
You don't have to answer
if it's too much pressure,

1121
00:46:07,031 --> 00:46:09,142
but do you feel like you've explored
your options enough?

1122
00:46:09,167 --> 00:46:11,035
- Do you feel completely sorted out?
- Yeah.

1123
00:46:13,671 --> 00:46:15,314
- He must be so nervous.
- Just confess already!

1124
00:46:15,339 --> 00:46:16,939
Am I still...

1125
00:46:17,008 --> 00:46:17,841
in your heart?

1126
00:46:18,242 --> 00:46:20,376
(That makes my heart flutter.)

1127
00:46:20,377 --> 00:46:22,845
"Am I still in your heart?"

1128
00:46:23,681 --> 00:46:25,181
Wow, what a line.

1129
00:46:26,284 --> 00:46:28,218
Am I still...

1130
00:46:28,219 --> 00:46:29,152
in your heart?

1131
00:46:29,153 --> 00:46:30,187
(Nodding)

1132
00:46:30,188 --> 00:46:31,021
I am?

1133
00:46:32,523 --> 00:46:34,457
After my date yesterday,

1134
00:46:35,560 --> 00:46:37,094
I actually thought about you a lot.

1135
00:46:38,029 --> 00:46:38,895
You did?

1136
00:46:40,130 --> 00:46:42,585
So, do you want to keep
getting to know me?

1137
00:46:42,610 --> 00:46:43,233
Yeah.

1138
00:46:43,234 --> 00:46:46,336
To be honest, I came to Yeon House...

1139
00:46:46,337 --> 00:46:48,438
open to meeting everyone.

1140
00:46:48,439 --> 00:46:50,640
I shouldn't have let it get to me,
but I did.

1141
00:46:51,108 --> 00:46:53,010
I'm the one who made you feel that way.

1142
00:46:53,411 --> 00:46:56,980
Because I only had eyes for you.

1143
00:46:57,348 --> 00:47:00,583
But I kept wondering sometimes.

1144
00:47:00,584 --> 00:47:01,384
About what?

1145
00:47:01,385 --> 00:47:03,486
- Why you're so hung up on me.
- Why I'm hung up on you?

1146
00:47:03,487 --> 00:47:05,188
Yes, because I honestly don't get it.

1147
00:47:05,189 --> 00:47:08,558
I know you really enjoyed our 1-on-1 date,

1148
00:47:08,793 --> 00:47:12,496
but that was purely based
on first impressions.

1149
00:47:12,863 --> 00:47:14,799
Was there really more to it after that?

1150
00:47:15,600 --> 00:47:17,234
I was just genuinely curious.

1151
00:47:17,735 --> 00:47:19,637
It indeed started
with my first impression.

1152
00:47:20,137 --> 00:47:21,439
Your calm vibe.

1153
00:47:21,672 --> 00:47:22,740
How pretty you are.

1154
00:47:23,140 --> 00:47:25,908
Everything about you is exactly my type.

1155
00:47:27,211 --> 00:47:29,879
From the literal moment I met you,

1156
00:47:30,281 --> 00:47:33,316
I've felt like it was always you.

1157
00:47:33,551 --> 00:47:35,285
And that hasn't changed.

1158
00:47:35,553 --> 00:47:36,954
She really is his exact type.

1159
00:47:38,256 --> 00:47:41,557
I feel like it means we're meant to be.

1160
00:47:41,959 --> 00:47:44,260
But if I ever made you uncomfortable,

1161
00:47:44,495 --> 00:47:45,328
I'm sorry.

1162
00:47:45,664 --> 00:47:47,364
I'm so glad they're finding
their way back to each other.

1163
00:47:47,365 --> 00:47:49,466
They're definitely dating after it aired.

1164
00:47:49,467 --> 00:47:51,135
- Without a doubt.
- But wait, what happens now?

1165
00:47:52,303 --> 00:47:54,271
Since my birthday is early in the year,

1166
00:47:54,538 --> 00:47:55,873
we're technically 12 years apart.

1167
00:47:56,007 --> 00:47:57,908
That's not even a big age gap.

1168
00:47:58,509 --> 00:47:59,744
What are you talking about?

1169
00:48:00,311 --> 00:48:02,746
What if I were 28?

1170
00:48:02,747 --> 00:48:03,889
That would be amazing.

1171
00:48:03,914 --> 00:48:05,191
- Really?
- Yeah, that'd be ideal.

1172
00:48:05,216 --> 00:48:06,784
How on earth are you the youngest?

1173
00:48:10,154 --> 00:48:10,920
Seriously, how?

1174
00:48:11,222 --> 00:48:12,957
How can you possibly be the youngest here?

1175
00:48:17,361 --> 00:48:19,529
I know, right? I hate being the youngest.

1176
00:48:23,801 --> 00:48:25,869
What does age even matter anyway?

1177
00:48:27,071 --> 00:48:28,338
So you really thought...

1178
00:48:29,540 --> 00:48:30,807
I was older than this?

1179
00:48:31,042 --> 00:48:31,808
Yes.

1180
00:48:32,376 --> 00:48:33,844
We might have a 12-year age gap,

1181
00:48:34,211 --> 00:48:37,280
but are you so sure we won't work out?

1182
00:48:37,581 --> 00:48:38,949
What do you mean by that?

1183
00:48:39,884 --> 00:48:41,952
Can you see our future?

1184
00:48:42,320 --> 00:48:43,487
- No.
- Exactly.

1185
00:48:43,688 --> 00:48:44,789
I just can't picture it.

1186
00:48:45,022 --> 00:48:46,222
- Our future together?
- Yeah.

1187
00:48:47,792 --> 00:48:49,727
Why are you closing yourself off to it?

1188
00:48:51,255 --> 00:48:53,163
(Just as they reconnect,
age gets in the way.)

1189
00:48:53,164 --> 00:48:54,498
We should keep an open mind.

1190
00:48:56,934 --> 00:49:00,203
I really don't think age matters
when it comes to love.

1191
00:49:00,637 --> 00:49:01,905
But I do understand...

1192
00:49:03,307 --> 00:49:05,475
why the other person would worry...

1193
00:49:05,876 --> 00:49:08,845
if the age gap feels too massive.

1194
00:49:09,114 --> 00:49:12,215
Now that I'm actually
sitting here talking to her,

1195
00:49:12,583 --> 00:49:13,383
reality is hitting me.

1196
00:49:13,384 --> 00:49:14,684
(The conversation gives him
a sharp reality check.)

1197
00:49:15,719 --> 00:49:19,188
(The two move to a new spot
to keep talking.)

1198
00:49:20,691 --> 00:49:23,594
I really should've done
the jacuzzi date with you.

1199
00:49:26,864 --> 00:49:27,664
What a missed opportunity.

1200
00:49:27,665 --> 00:49:29,500
I know. I wish it had happened
a day later.

1201
00:49:29,667 --> 00:49:30,333
Wait, what?

1202
00:49:30,334 --> 00:49:32,736
- That really should've been a day later.
- She wishes it happened a day later.

1203
00:49:33,738 --> 00:49:35,260
Since time is running out,

1204
00:49:35,284 --> 00:49:37,141
everyone's going to make
their final choice.

1205
00:49:37,276 --> 00:49:39,710
- Wait, really?
- Everyone is locking in their targets.

1206
00:49:40,878 --> 00:49:42,145
We're down to the wire.

1207
00:49:42,146 --> 00:49:43,279
(Time is running out at Yeon House.)

1208
00:49:43,280 --> 00:49:44,582
Everyone looks so determined.

1209
00:49:46,650 --> 00:49:49,352
The timing is insane.
I'm dying to know what happens.

1210
00:49:49,353 --> 00:49:51,822
Should I go sneak a peek
and pretend I'm grabbing something?

1211
00:49:52,289 --> 00:49:53,956
- Are you tipsy?
- No way.

1212
00:49:53,957 --> 00:49:56,425
No, I'm just a little...

1213
00:49:56,961 --> 00:49:58,361
(Worried)

1214
00:49:58,362 --> 00:49:59,095
Alright then.

1215
00:49:59,630 --> 00:50:01,532
Your liver's still holding up great.

1216
00:50:03,175 --> 00:50:05,075
But mine isn't.

1217
00:50:08,309 --> 00:50:09,175
Want a piece of mine?

1218
00:50:09,509 --> 00:50:10,509
- What?
- I can give you a piece.

1219
00:50:10,509 --> 00:50:11,875
- Give me what?
- A piece of my liver?

1220
00:50:13,801 --> 00:50:15,101
(What did he say?)

1221
00:50:15,609 --> 00:50:16,442
Goodness!

1222
00:50:17,109 --> 00:50:18,409
What is he even saying?

1223
00:50:18,434 --> 00:50:20,300
- Is this liver flirting?
- "Want me to give you part of mine?"

1224
00:50:20,809 --> 00:50:22,242
Is he flirting with his liver?

1225
00:50:22,242 --> 00:50:24,342
"Ju Hee, my liver is really young."

1226
00:50:24,342 --> 00:50:26,209
"I'll give you part of it,
so live a long life."

1227
00:50:27,142 --> 00:50:31,475
I'm officially rooting for Yun So now.

1228
00:50:32,775 --> 00:50:33,609
You want it?

1229
00:50:33,975 --> 00:50:34,909
What?

1230
00:50:34,909 --> 00:50:36,309
- Give me what?
- A part of my liver?

1231
00:50:38,142 --> 00:50:39,742
(Eyes wide open)

1232
00:50:39,742 --> 00:50:40,509
Are you kidding?

1233
00:50:40,509 --> 00:50:42,842
- No, I mean it.
- Are you serious?

1234
00:50:42,842 --> 00:50:43,809
I'd give you part of my liver.

1235
00:50:43,809 --> 00:50:44,975
- Really?
- Yes.

1236
00:50:46,642 --> 00:50:48,809
- He genuinely means it when he says that.
- Of course. At that stage,

1237
00:50:48,809 --> 00:50:50,342
it feels like you'd even die
for the other person.

1238
00:50:50,342 --> 00:50:52,042
(While Yun So is flirting with his liver)

1239
00:50:52,309 --> 00:50:55,575
(Ji Hye, Jin Woo, and Jung Won remain
in the common room.)

1240
00:50:55,575 --> 00:50:57,475
I think I've talked
to every guy 1-on-1 now.

1241
00:51:00,275 --> 00:51:01,442
I've completely made up my mind.

1242
00:51:01,942 --> 00:51:03,742
I'm done now.

1243
00:51:04,142 --> 00:51:05,609
You've already decided? That was fast.

1244
00:51:06,442 --> 00:51:09,776
I have. For sure.

1245
00:51:10,642 --> 00:51:13,409
- It's not Jin Woo, for sure.
- It's not.

1246
00:51:13,409 --> 00:51:14,809
Are you guys still trying
to figure things out?

1247
00:51:17,684 --> 00:51:18,642
But why?

1248
00:51:18,642 --> 00:51:20,375
Hasn't everyone made up their minds
by now?

1249
00:51:21,275 --> 00:51:23,909
(Glancing)

1250
00:51:27,742 --> 00:51:29,775
Please leave.

1251
00:51:30,809 --> 00:51:31,642
What?

1252
00:51:31,942 --> 00:51:34,075
Seriously? I can't believe my eyes.

1253
00:51:34,384 --> 00:51:36,217
What on earth has happened to him?

1254
00:51:36,242 --> 00:51:37,742
Jin Woo!

1255
00:51:37,742 --> 00:51:39,975
After the age reveal,
he's suddenly acting so bold.

1256
00:51:40,442 --> 00:51:41,475
(Slouching)

1257
00:51:41,684 --> 00:51:43,884
"Leave!"

1258
00:51:43,909 --> 00:51:45,909
I can't believe he said that
with a face that handsome.

1259
00:51:46,442 --> 00:51:48,342
Please leave.

1260
00:51:49,509 --> 00:51:51,575
I guess I should step out.

1261
00:51:51,649 --> 00:51:54,383
(Jin Woo wants some alone time
with Ji Hye.)

1262
00:51:56,509 --> 00:52:01,042
(Jung Won gives them some space.)

1263
00:52:01,942 --> 00:52:03,642
(Now that they're alone,
what will Jin Woo say?)

1264
00:52:03,642 --> 00:52:05,475
What's he going to say?

1265
00:52:06,909 --> 00:52:08,975
(Glaring)

1266
00:52:09,275 --> 00:52:10,342
What did you want to talk about?

1267
00:52:10,909 --> 00:52:11,842
Well...

1268
00:52:13,442 --> 00:52:16,509
- You said you've made up your mind.
- Right.

1269
00:52:17,404 --> 00:52:18,904
I just want to hear about it.

1270
00:52:19,937 --> 00:52:21,037
You're asking me that so directly?

1271
00:52:21,037 --> 00:52:22,370
If it's not me,
I'd rather you just tell me.

1272
00:52:23,370 --> 00:52:28,204
But if you still haven't decided
on anyone, then...

1273
00:52:29,037 --> 00:52:30,704
Jin Woo is exhausted.

1274
00:52:30,704 --> 00:52:32,270
Of course he is.

1275
00:52:32,270 --> 00:52:34,199
He's probably wondering how much longer
he has to keep doing this!

1276
00:52:34,200 --> 00:52:36,037
He's already done everything he could.

1277
00:52:36,037 --> 00:52:38,704
When I got here earlier
and came straight over to ask you,

1278
00:52:39,437 --> 00:52:40,970
you said you'd tell me once you were sure.

1279
00:52:40,970 --> 00:52:45,437
So I think it's okay to tell me now.

1280
00:52:47,070 --> 00:52:48,470
You already know.

1281
00:52:48,470 --> 00:52:50,570
No matter what you say, what can I do?

1282
00:52:51,204 --> 00:52:53,170
He must be having a really hard time!

1283
00:52:56,070 --> 00:52:59,337
I'm not clueless.

1284
00:52:59,337 --> 00:53:00,499
I have a pretty good idea how you feel.

1285
00:53:00,737 --> 00:53:02,337
He says he kind of knows it.

1286
00:53:02,337 --> 00:53:04,070
(Nodding)

1287
00:53:04,070 --> 00:53:05,304
Oh, dear.

1288
00:53:07,204 --> 00:53:09,304
I'm not sure
whether your intuition is right, but...

1289
00:53:11,370 --> 00:53:13,470
(Hesitating)

1290
00:53:13,470 --> 00:53:14,304
Please.

1291
00:53:16,970 --> 00:53:18,737
Because the person you've chosen isn't me?

1292
00:53:19,237 --> 00:53:20,037
Yes.

1293
00:53:21,470 --> 00:53:22,370
You're right.

1294
00:53:23,970 --> 00:53:26,204
(There's no place for Jin Woo
in Ji Hye's heart.)

1295
00:53:26,204 --> 00:53:28,837
Oh, no. I feel so bad.

1296
00:53:30,970 --> 00:53:32,004
Does that answer your question?

1297
00:53:33,170 --> 00:53:35,937
Oh, no. He can't hide
the look on his face.

1298
00:53:36,570 --> 00:53:37,504
Was it enough?

1299
00:53:37,504 --> 00:53:38,937
(Nodding)

1300
00:53:45,570 --> 00:53:46,470
Are you going to drink more?

1301
00:53:47,804 --> 00:53:49,104
No. I'm done drinking.

1302
00:53:53,037 --> 00:53:55,237
Do you feel uncomfortable around me
because you feel sorry for me?

1303
00:53:57,004 --> 00:53:58,937
It's not that I'm uncomfortable.

1304
00:53:58,937 --> 00:54:01,037
I just don't know what to say...

1305
00:54:03,137 --> 00:54:06,704
when we're having this conversation.

1306
00:54:07,604 --> 00:54:08,470
I'm only human.

1307
00:54:12,004 --> 00:54:16,437
How could I not feel sorry?

1308
00:54:16,437 --> 00:54:17,637
Of course, she feels bad.

1309
00:54:17,637 --> 00:54:20,970
I guess I made you feel that way.

1310
00:54:21,870 --> 00:54:26,204
No. I'm grateful that you were
so honest with me,

1311
00:54:26,204 --> 00:54:27,837
and I think it took a lot of courage.

1312
00:54:28,570 --> 00:54:31,770
That's why I could be honest with you...

1313
00:54:32,337 --> 00:54:34,170
instead of beating around the bush.

1314
00:54:37,370 --> 00:54:39,570
But did I ever lead you on?

1315
00:54:40,104 --> 00:54:42,370
Not once. I just followed my heart
the whole time.

1316
00:54:42,870 --> 00:54:43,904
Not at all.

1317
00:54:44,104 --> 00:54:46,104
Oh, goodness!

1318
00:54:49,704 --> 00:54:52,237
(Sighing)

1319
00:54:59,970 --> 00:55:06,137
(Jin Woo's feelings never reached her.)

1320
00:55:12,104 --> 00:55:13,137
I should go to bed now.

1321
00:55:14,404 --> 00:55:15,370
When are you going to bed?

1322
00:55:16,437 --> 00:55:17,304
In a little while.

1323
00:55:22,404 --> 00:55:23,270
Good night.

1324
00:55:24,537 --> 00:55:26,904
- Good night. See you tomorrow.
- See you tomorrow.

1325
00:55:35,237 --> 00:55:37,137
She didn't beat around the bush.

1326
00:55:37,137 --> 00:55:39,304
But she told me honestly how she felt.

1327
00:55:39,770 --> 00:55:42,070
Over the past four days,

1328
00:55:42,812 --> 00:55:48,370
I gave her everything I possibly could,

1329
00:55:49,204 --> 00:55:50,704
so I don't have any regrets.

1330
00:55:50,704 --> 00:55:53,604
Even if I could go back in time,
I know I'd do exactly the same thing.

1331
00:55:54,404 --> 00:55:55,937
Now I'm going to accept it.

1332
00:55:55,937 --> 00:55:57,104
And I've been thinking...

1333
00:55:57,104 --> 00:55:59,170
more about what I'm going
to do from here on.

1334
00:56:01,304 --> 00:56:03,237
Four days can feel this long.

1335
00:56:03,237 --> 00:56:05,670
(Where will Jin Woo's heart go now?)

1336
00:56:06,570 --> 00:56:10,470
(Ji Hye returns to her room.)

1337
00:56:12,604 --> 00:56:14,170
(Sighing)

1338
00:56:17,137 --> 00:56:19,970
(She seems lost in thought.)

1339
00:56:19,970 --> 00:56:21,604
This has to be hard for Ji Hye too.

1340
00:56:27,370 --> 00:56:31,437
Jung Won and Jun Han are
the two people in my heart.

1341
00:56:31,970 --> 00:56:33,637
It's Jung Won and Jun Han?

1342
00:56:34,204 --> 00:56:38,104
(Ji Hye's heart belongs
to Jung Won and Jun Han.)

1343
00:56:38,570 --> 00:56:41,704
(Meanwhile, Jin Young and Jung Won are
out for a walk.)

1344
00:56:42,037 --> 00:56:43,870
- How did it go with Jun Han?
- With Jun Han?

1345
00:56:46,237 --> 00:56:47,737
Did anything change?

1346
00:56:48,237 --> 00:56:49,370
- Change?
- Yes.

1347
00:56:50,404 --> 00:56:54,070
(He's curious about what Jin Young
and Jun Han talked about.)

1348
00:56:54,570 --> 00:56:57,337
I was just honest with him.

1349
00:56:57,337 --> 00:57:00,104
- You were?
- Yes, I was honest.

1350
00:57:00,104 --> 00:57:01,170
I see.

1351
00:57:02,004 --> 00:57:03,137
What do you mean by honest?

1352
00:57:05,704 --> 00:57:07,337
Well, the first thing I did
was apologize to him.

1353
00:57:08,637 --> 00:57:14,504
(Earlier, Jin Young met with Jun Han
before talking to Jung Won.)

1354
00:57:15,937 --> 00:57:17,770
(Hesitating)

1355
00:57:18,437 --> 00:57:19,937
So, did you have fun?

1356
00:57:20,604 --> 00:57:22,370
Actually,

1357
00:57:23,870 --> 00:57:27,270
I'd started to like him more,
and I wanted to get to know him better.

1358
00:57:28,370 --> 00:57:31,637
She handles these situations really well.

1359
00:57:31,637 --> 00:57:32,504
That's what I said.

1360
00:57:33,304 --> 00:57:35,127
Just tell me honestly.

1361
00:57:35,904 --> 00:57:39,504
Actually, I felt really sorry
toward you for two days.

1362
00:57:39,504 --> 00:57:41,604
But I think being honest is
the right thing to do.

1363
00:57:41,904 --> 00:57:44,737
I truly meant what I just told you.

1364
00:57:44,737 --> 00:57:47,670
(Jin Young was honest with Jun Han
about how she felt.)

1365
00:57:47,670 --> 00:57:48,504
Yes.

1366
00:57:49,904 --> 00:57:50,870
I told Jun Han,

1367
00:57:53,537 --> 00:57:57,004
"I don't see you romantically yet,"

1368
00:57:59,270 --> 00:58:00,870
"but when I went on a date
with Jung Won today,"

1369
00:58:01,470 --> 00:58:04,304
"I felt attracted to him."

1370
00:58:06,737 --> 00:58:07,704
I like that.

1371
00:58:08,404 --> 00:58:10,437
- That's what I said.
- Is that so?

1372
00:58:10,437 --> 00:58:11,204
Yes.

1373
00:58:12,237 --> 00:58:14,870
But whenever everyone's together,
you never show any interest in me.

1374
00:58:14,870 --> 00:58:15,870
You don't even come near me.

1375
00:58:15,870 --> 00:58:17,237
Why do you keep your distance?

1376
00:58:17,870 --> 00:58:19,437
- That is...
- Are you shy?

1377
00:58:19,870 --> 00:58:21,370
I just...

1378
00:58:21,870 --> 00:58:23,837
I just don't know.

1379
00:58:23,837 --> 00:58:26,970
But why do I feel so self-conscious
around everyone?

1380
00:58:26,970 --> 00:58:27,737
Why?

1381
00:58:29,170 --> 00:58:30,537
I don't even know why.

1382
00:58:31,537 --> 00:58:34,570
I'll try to be a little braver.

1383
00:58:35,470 --> 00:58:37,904
You have to go after what you want.

1384
00:58:37,904 --> 00:58:39,337
- Me? Me after you?
- Yes.

1385
00:58:39,870 --> 00:58:42,337
I'm trying to win you over right now,

1386
00:58:42,870 --> 00:58:44,604
so shouldn't you be trying
to win me over too?

1387
00:58:45,370 --> 00:58:47,404
What on earth did he just say?

1388
00:58:49,170 --> 00:58:49,970
No?

1389
00:58:50,737 --> 00:58:52,870
(Staring)

1390
00:58:52,870 --> 00:58:54,004
They might end up kissing.

1391
00:58:54,970 --> 00:58:55,904
What's that?

1392
00:58:56,437 --> 00:58:57,470
It just feels...

1393
00:59:00,004 --> 00:59:03,437
(They confirm
that the feelings are mutual.)

1394
00:59:03,437 --> 00:59:05,051
You may be an older woman to me
when we're here.

1395
00:59:05,270 --> 00:59:06,772
But the moment we leave,
you'll just be a woman.

1396
00:59:10,170 --> 00:59:11,170
You'll see me after we leave?

1397
00:59:11,470 --> 00:59:12,337
Of course.

1398
00:59:14,204 --> 00:59:15,004
Okay.

1399
00:59:15,004 --> 00:59:18,270
(They made a promise
that's just between the two of them.)

1400
00:59:18,370 --> 00:59:21,104
Unlike Jun Han, she said she was attracted
to me romantically.

1401
00:59:21,696 --> 00:59:26,162
After hearing that, I felt reassured,

1402
00:59:26,704 --> 00:59:30,637
and my confidence in her went up
to about 80 percent.

1403
00:59:32,637 --> 00:59:35,437
Good night. See you tomorrow.

1404
00:59:36,170 --> 00:59:37,737
So, having conversations was
really important.

1405
00:59:38,937 --> 00:59:42,070
(Jin Young is on her way back
to her room.)

1406
00:59:43,004 --> 00:59:44,170
- Jin Young.
- Yes?

1407
00:59:44,604 --> 00:59:45,837
Isn't that Jin Woo's voice?

1408
00:59:46,170 --> 00:59:47,204
Why are you still out?

1409
00:59:47,204 --> 00:59:48,304
Me?

1410
00:59:48,304 --> 00:59:49,237
Are you wandering?

1411
00:59:50,004 --> 00:59:51,737
- I was on my way back in.
- Were you waiting for someone?

1412
00:59:51,737 --> 00:59:54,237
- No, I was on my way back.
- Come on in.

1413
00:59:54,837 --> 00:59:56,070
- No one is here now.
- Okay.

1414
00:59:57,770 --> 00:59:59,604
Jin Woo and Jin Young?

1415
01:00:01,841 --> 01:00:02,674
For me,

1416
01:00:04,410 --> 01:00:05,343
Season One is done.

1417
01:00:06,712 --> 01:00:07,745
Does that mean there's a two?

1418
01:00:08,247 --> 01:00:10,515
What do you mean Season One is over?

1419
01:00:10,750 --> 01:00:13,218
- Me and Ji Hye...
- You're done?

1420
01:00:13,652 --> 01:00:14,518
You're done?

1421
01:00:14,519 --> 01:00:16,420
(Nodding)

1422
01:00:17,556 --> 01:00:19,156
She told me directly.

1423
01:00:22,028 --> 01:00:22,828
Are you okay?

1424
01:00:23,195 --> 01:00:23,961
Well...

1425
01:00:25,899 --> 01:00:27,365
It's not like my life is over.

1426
01:00:27,366 --> 01:00:31,636
(Jin Woo forces a smile.)

1427
01:00:33,106 --> 01:00:34,272
You're being cool about it.

1428
01:00:34,440 --> 01:00:35,928
You're being really cool about it.

1429
01:00:35,929 --> 01:00:37,142
- There are more fish in the sea.
- True.

1430
01:00:37,143 --> 01:00:38,877
But you've done your best.

1431
01:00:38,878 --> 01:00:39,944
You've expressed everything.

1432
01:00:40,746 --> 01:00:41,646
Can you tell?

1433
01:00:42,248 --> 01:00:43,515
There's nothing more you could've done.

1434
01:00:44,016 --> 01:00:45,583
Nothing more you can do.

1435
01:00:45,584 --> 01:00:47,819
- That's true.
- Thanks for recognizing that.

1436
01:00:47,820 --> 01:00:49,988
I'm proud of you.

1437
01:00:49,989 --> 01:00:50,822
(She comforts him.)

1438
01:00:50,823 --> 01:00:52,123
Jin Young is really nice.

1439
01:00:53,125 --> 01:00:55,627
(Heavy-hearted)

1440
01:00:56,729 --> 01:00:59,497
We came here to get to know each other...

1441
01:00:59,498 --> 01:01:02,701
and develop feelings for each other.

1442
01:01:03,302 --> 01:01:08,206
But if there's no one that you want
to get to know or to like,

1443
01:01:08,207 --> 01:01:10,909
there's really no need to force things.

1444
01:01:11,343 --> 01:01:12,743
There's really no need.

1445
01:01:13,412 --> 01:01:14,145
But...

1446
01:01:14,880 --> 01:01:16,882
there are more dates remaining.

1447
01:01:17,283 --> 01:01:21,086
For the sake of the person
who is on a date with you,

1448
01:01:21,087 --> 01:01:23,555
just try to have fun, whoever that may be.

1449
01:01:23,556 --> 01:01:26,858
It'll just be good to keep that in mind.

1450
01:01:27,660 --> 01:01:31,063
If you're on a date and you hit it off,

1451
01:01:31,064 --> 01:01:32,364
then that's great.

1452
01:01:34,500 --> 01:01:35,700
It could be you.

1453
01:01:37,169 --> 01:01:38,002
What?

1454
01:01:40,840 --> 01:01:42,407
No, but...

1455
01:01:42,408 --> 01:01:45,911
there are remaining dates left.

1456
01:01:45,912 --> 01:01:47,379
Jin Woo...

1457
01:01:47,713 --> 01:01:49,781
can't just decide not to go on dates...

1458
01:01:49,782 --> 01:01:50,915
and just stay at the house.

1459
01:01:51,183 --> 01:01:53,684
So he just means
that he could ask her out.

1460
01:01:53,986 --> 01:01:57,188
Maybe he's open
to get to know other people.

1461
01:01:58,557 --> 01:02:02,460
It could be you.

1462
01:02:02,928 --> 01:02:03,928
- Me?
- Yes.

1463
01:02:03,929 --> 01:02:04,762
Okay.

1464
01:02:05,297 --> 01:02:08,065
Because I've been comfortable with you.

1465
01:02:08,467 --> 01:02:10,034
Yes, you have.

1466
01:02:10,035 --> 01:02:11,269
And vice versa.

1467
01:02:11,270 --> 01:02:12,804
We talked about the weirdest things.

1468
01:02:12,805 --> 01:02:14,005
So I'm saying...

1469
01:02:14,473 --> 01:02:16,107
I didn't see you with potential.

1470
01:02:16,108 --> 01:02:17,909
So I'm guessing...

1471
01:02:18,177 --> 01:02:20,311
you all thought
that I was just interested in Ji Hye.

1472
01:02:20,646 --> 01:02:22,080
And that makes you comfortable around me.

1473
01:02:22,081 --> 01:02:23,181
That happens.

1474
01:02:23,182 --> 01:02:25,450
(Jin Woo hasn't had eyes
for anyone other than Ji Hye so far.)

1475
01:02:26,252 --> 01:02:30,989
(Can Jin Woo make a fresh start?)

1476
01:02:31,624 --> 01:02:32,524
Where do you want to go?

1477
01:02:32,525 --> 01:02:33,926
Is anyone in the Talk Room?

1478
01:02:33,927 --> 01:02:35,026
Let's see.

1479
01:02:35,127 --> 01:02:36,294
I've never been here.

1480
01:02:36,295 --> 01:02:37,528
- Oh, really?
- Yes.

1481
01:02:37,830 --> 01:02:39,497
- I see!
- It's nice here.

1482
01:02:43,369 --> 01:02:44,836
- I see.
- It's a present.

1483
01:02:45,938 --> 01:02:47,906
- What is it?
- He's going to make her cry.

1484
01:02:48,241 --> 01:02:50,008
Did you just pull it from your pocket?

1485
01:02:50,009 --> 01:02:50,909
No.

1486
01:02:50,910 --> 01:02:52,410
I brought it for you.

1487
01:02:52,411 --> 01:02:53,511
We can each take one.

1488
01:02:54,380 --> 01:02:56,648
Thank you. We should take it now.

1489
01:02:56,649 --> 01:02:57,782
Sure, let's do it.

1490
01:02:59,818 --> 01:03:01,719
Did I look too shocked?

1491
01:03:02,221 --> 01:03:03,955
It was obvious that you were.

1492
01:03:03,956 --> 01:03:04,856
Really?

1493
01:03:06,559 --> 01:03:08,627
There was no way you weren't shocked.

1494
01:03:09,628 --> 01:03:11,729
Your energy level was very different.

1495
01:03:12,600 --> 01:03:13,497
(Taking the vitamin he gave.)

1496
01:03:13,498 --> 01:03:16,667
You were talking about making drinks
and having drinks together.

1497
01:03:16,668 --> 01:03:17,701
Then you went silent.

1498
01:03:17,871 --> 01:03:19,304
I couldn't help being shocked.

1499
01:03:21,207 --> 01:03:24,376
It's understandable if you've never
dated a younger guy.

1500
01:03:25,144 --> 01:03:26,811
Was I your first pick?

1501
01:03:27,179 --> 01:03:28,813
Is that why you were shocked?

1502
01:03:29,114 --> 01:03:31,482
- He's making sure.
- Nice, Si Won.

1503
01:03:33,319 --> 01:03:36,087
As of yesterday, yes.

1504
01:03:36,188 --> 01:03:37,688
As of yesterday?

1505
01:03:37,790 --> 01:03:39,157
- The pool?
- Right.

1506
01:03:39,425 --> 01:03:41,793
Are you contemplating?

1507
01:03:42,261 --> 01:03:43,795
Honestly, until now,

1508
01:03:43,796 --> 01:03:45,496
I've been contemplating a lot.

1509
01:03:46,265 --> 01:03:48,600
Because I've talked to Ji Seung a lot.

1510
01:03:48,601 --> 01:03:50,001
So to an extent,

1511
01:03:50,002 --> 01:03:51,269
- I got to know her.
- Sure.

1512
01:03:52,004 --> 01:03:54,973
And I was on a date with Ji Hye today,

1513
01:03:54,974 --> 01:03:57,108
so I've gotten to know her as well.

1514
01:03:57,309 --> 01:03:59,377
Among the three people
that I wanted to get to know,

1515
01:03:59,378 --> 01:04:01,513
you're the only one I haven't
talked to 1-on-1.

1516
01:04:02,147 --> 01:04:03,748
That's true.

1517
01:04:03,749 --> 01:04:04,982
I hope they work out.

1518
01:04:05,651 --> 01:04:08,319
So I thought I should really try
to talk to you today.

1519
01:04:08,988 --> 01:04:10,989
I wrote you down
as my first choice yesterday.

1520
01:04:10,990 --> 01:04:11,823
Did you?

1521
01:04:12,891 --> 01:04:15,793
I really wanted to converse
with you a lot as well.

1522
01:04:16,095 --> 01:04:20,498
Ever since the pool yesterday,

1523
01:04:20,499 --> 01:04:23,334
I felt like you were taking care of me.

1524
01:04:23,335 --> 01:04:25,270
I think that's when it started
for me as well.

1525
01:04:25,271 --> 01:04:26,604
Exactly.

1526
01:04:26,605 --> 01:04:28,807
I thought you were good
at taking care of people.

1527
01:04:29,008 --> 01:04:31,309
There was something between them there.

1528
01:04:31,310 --> 01:04:33,712
He blocked the waves for her and stuff.

1529
01:04:34,380 --> 01:04:37,549
So I think I've gotten more interested.

1530
01:04:39,051 --> 01:04:41,386
That's why I chose you yesterday.

1531
01:04:41,420 --> 01:04:42,620
- Really?
- Yes.

1532
01:04:43,389 --> 01:04:44,255
Even today.

1533
01:04:44,556 --> 01:04:46,757
(Yu Jin and Si Won are drawn
to each other.)

1534
01:04:46,758 --> 01:04:48,325
They're really compatible.

1535
01:04:48,961 --> 01:04:50,695
I told Ji Seung...

1536
01:04:50,696 --> 01:04:52,830
that I wanted to talk to you.

1537
01:04:52,831 --> 01:04:54,465
Because you seem so consistent.

1538
01:04:54,900 --> 01:04:55,900
You don't seem to waver a lot,

1539
01:04:56,669 --> 01:04:59,671
and I do prefer such people.

1540
01:04:59,672 --> 01:05:01,706
- Yes, I don't waver a lot.
- Right?

1541
01:05:01,907 --> 01:05:03,607
I told her I wanted to talk to you.

1542
01:05:03,876 --> 01:05:06,644
I wanted to talk to you,
then our ages were revealed.

1543
01:05:07,713 --> 01:05:08,613
I know.

1544
01:05:08,614 --> 01:05:11,683
(So cruel)

1545
01:05:12,484 --> 01:05:14,419
I didn't expect our ages
to be revealed so quickly.

1546
01:05:14,486 --> 01:05:15,486
So...

1547
01:05:15,821 --> 01:05:18,122
having the 12-year age gap worried me.

1548
01:05:18,123 --> 01:05:20,090
I thought you might change your mind...

1549
01:05:21,093 --> 01:05:22,860
because of the age gap.

1550
01:05:24,163 --> 01:05:25,329
What do you think?

1551
01:05:25,330 --> 01:05:26,831
You've dated older women,

1552
01:05:26,832 --> 01:05:29,567
but not with someone with such a huge gap.

1553
01:05:29,835 --> 01:05:31,302
Yes, five years maximum.

1554
01:05:31,303 --> 01:05:32,103
Right?

1555
01:05:32,905 --> 01:05:35,874
How do you feel about the 12-year gap?

1556
01:05:35,875 --> 01:05:36,674
Twelve years?

1557
01:05:36,842 --> 01:05:37,942
(The unmentionable is mentioned)

1558
01:05:37,943 --> 01:05:41,112
As she asks that question,

1559
01:05:41,113 --> 01:05:44,082
she herself thinks it's absurd.

1560
01:05:44,083 --> 01:05:46,350
There's a guy you're interested in...

1561
01:05:46,351 --> 01:05:48,586
without knowing his age.
Then you find out you're 12 years apart.

1562
01:05:48,587 --> 01:05:51,088
Even if my life depended on it,

1563
01:05:51,089 --> 01:05:52,857
I could never bring myself to say...

1564
01:05:52,858 --> 01:05:54,292
the words "Chinese Zodiac sign" at all.

1565
01:05:54,293 --> 01:05:55,426
That means...

1566
01:05:55,427 --> 01:05:57,562
I'd feel like the personification
of the zodiac sign.

1567
01:05:58,397 --> 01:05:59,664
(Giggling)

1568
01:05:59,665 --> 01:06:02,133
Yu Jin is really brave for it.

1569
01:06:02,234 --> 01:06:03,401
She mustered up courage.

1570
01:06:04,202 --> 01:06:07,004
How do you feel about the 12-year gap?

1571
01:06:07,005 --> 01:06:07,872
Twelve years?

1572
01:06:09,675 --> 01:06:12,610
Not starting anything
just because of age feels wrong.

1573
01:06:13,011 --> 01:06:16,647
- What?
- It'd be good to go on a date.

1574
01:06:16,849 --> 01:06:18,516
I'd like to go on a date with you.

1575
01:06:18,917 --> 01:06:19,917
How?

1576
01:06:20,286 --> 01:06:21,819
- How?
- Yes.

1577
01:06:22,554 --> 01:06:24,088
When we get a chance tomorrow.

1578
01:06:26,959 --> 01:06:28,927
We should go on a date.

1579
01:06:28,928 --> 01:06:31,329
Yes, going on a date is different
from a 1-on-1 conversation as well.

1580
01:06:31,330 --> 01:06:32,964
It is different.

1581
01:06:33,899 --> 01:06:35,199
The tide has turned.

1582
01:06:35,567 --> 01:06:36,700
Toward Si Won.

1583
01:06:36,802 --> 01:06:38,302
- She's at ease.
- Yes.

1584
01:06:38,537 --> 01:06:41,672
Are there no more people
that you want to talk to?

1585
01:06:42,441 --> 01:06:44,542
No. I don't think so.

1586
01:06:44,543 --> 01:06:45,376
- Really?
- Yes.

1587
01:06:45,377 --> 01:06:49,647
- No. I don't think so.
- Really?

1588
01:06:51,717 --> 01:06:55,887
When I'm with Si Won,
I don't feel the age gap.

1589
01:06:56,221 --> 01:06:59,957
I think that's why I felt okay with it.

1590
01:07:02,227 --> 01:07:03,527
Should we go now?

1591
01:07:03,796 --> 01:07:04,662
Okay.

1592
01:07:04,663 --> 01:07:06,197
It's time for bed.

1593
01:07:06,198 --> 01:07:07,532
Great conversation.

1594
01:07:10,402 --> 01:07:12,003
Are there people not sleeping yet?

1595
01:07:12,004 --> 01:07:13,084
I wonder.

1596
01:07:13,085 --> 01:07:14,105
(The distance closes between them.)

1597
01:07:14,106 --> 01:07:15,173
This is so nice.

1598
01:07:15,707 --> 01:07:17,074
I'm excited for tomorrow.

1599
01:07:17,742 --> 01:07:20,477
(Yu Jin is back in her room.)

1600
01:07:20,545 --> 01:07:21,378
So cold.

1601
01:07:23,615 --> 01:07:26,083
Yu Jin and Ji Seung share the same room!

1602
01:07:26,418 --> 01:07:29,286
(That's true!)

1603
01:07:29,955 --> 01:07:32,323
Where have you been? With Jun Han?

1604
01:07:32,758 --> 01:07:34,859
No, I was with...

1605
01:07:34,860 --> 01:07:35,727
No!

1606
01:07:35,728 --> 01:07:36,394
Who?

1607
01:07:36,762 --> 01:07:37,695
Oh, no!

1608
01:07:38,130 --> 01:07:39,564
- Jung Won?
- No.

1609
01:07:39,898 --> 01:07:40,665
What?

1610
01:07:40,666 --> 01:07:42,700
- Si Won?
- Yes, I was talking to Si Won.

1611
01:07:42,701 --> 01:07:44,535
Wow. What did you talk about?

1612
01:07:45,170 --> 01:07:49,106
Just our age gap. How we feel about it.

1613
01:07:49,341 --> 01:07:50,941
Things like that.

1614
01:07:50,942 --> 01:07:52,543
Why would he ask you that...

1615
01:07:52,544 --> 01:07:54,145
and not ask me?

1616
01:07:56,682 --> 01:07:59,417
I should talk to Si Won.

1617
01:07:59,618 --> 01:08:01,719
Yes, talk to him.

1618
01:08:02,387 --> 01:08:04,221
- Where did you guys talk?
- The Talk Room.

1619
01:08:04,823 --> 01:08:05,890
What did you do there?

1620
01:08:06,325 --> 01:08:08,860
Did he go back to his room?

1621
01:08:08,861 --> 01:08:11,062
- Yes, he turned in.
- It's so late.

1622
01:08:11,830 --> 01:08:12,830
Talk to him tomorrow.

1623
01:08:12,831 --> 01:08:13,764
It's better that way.

1624
01:08:13,765 --> 01:08:15,800
I pretended on purpose.

1625
01:08:16,101 --> 01:08:17,835
What's the point of talking about it?

1626
01:08:19,004 --> 01:08:21,238
I think he thought I was about 30.

1627
01:08:21,239 --> 01:08:22,173
Oh, really?

1628
01:08:22,174 --> 01:08:24,875
Yes, 30 or maybe 31.

1629
01:08:25,143 --> 01:08:27,979
It didn't seem like he cared
about age very much.

1630
01:08:27,980 --> 01:08:30,547
- What?
- He doesn't care about age.

1631
01:08:30,548 --> 01:08:31,615
The vigor of a 25-year-old.

1632
01:08:31,616 --> 01:08:34,418
He thought the gap was okay
up to 12 years.

1633
01:08:34,686 --> 01:08:37,187
When I talked to Si Won...

1634
01:08:37,188 --> 01:08:38,322
Okay.

1635
01:08:38,323 --> 01:08:40,491
It's funny you talked to him at this hour.

1636
01:08:42,861 --> 01:08:44,962
I don't know how you'd feel...

1637
01:08:45,407 --> 01:08:46,497
when I talked to Si Won.

1638
01:08:46,498 --> 01:08:49,032
I felt like I didn't really have
to talk to Jun Han anymore.

1639
01:08:49,601 --> 01:08:51,468
In just a few hours?

1640
01:08:51,469 --> 01:08:53,704
I felt more comfortable talking...

1641
01:08:53,705 --> 01:08:55,339
to Si Won than I thought.

1642
01:08:55,607 --> 01:08:57,575
Are you set on Si Won now?

1643
01:08:57,576 --> 01:09:00,377
Yes. I think that's it for me.

1644
01:09:01,480 --> 01:09:03,481
The more I talk to him,

1645
01:09:03,882 --> 01:09:06,917
I could tell he doesn't waver much.

1646
01:09:06,918 --> 01:09:09,987
But doesn't that mean he wavers
when he's been talking to me?

1647
01:09:09,988 --> 01:09:10,754
Goodness.

1648
01:09:10,755 --> 01:09:12,256
Well, you should talk to him.

1649
01:09:12,658 --> 01:09:14,158
I'm fine. Don't mind me.

1650
01:09:14,159 --> 01:09:15,693
Well, I talked to him today.

1651
01:09:15,694 --> 01:09:18,363
Don't you mean you're going
to talk to him more?

1652
01:09:18,364 --> 01:09:19,998
Isn't that why you're telling me...

1653
01:09:20,465 --> 01:09:22,733
you don't know how I'd feel?

1654
01:09:23,135 --> 01:09:24,435
That you're set on Si Won?

1655
01:09:24,436 --> 01:09:25,803
Yes, that's what I mean.

1656
01:09:26,071 --> 01:09:28,539
My roommate Yu Jin came back...

1657
01:09:28,540 --> 01:09:30,741
and basically declared war,

1658
01:09:31,109 --> 01:09:32,376
saying that she's going
to get to know him.

1659
01:09:32,377 --> 01:09:34,878
At least that's how it felt.

1660
01:09:34,913 --> 01:09:38,249
I felt like she was trying to check me.

1661
01:09:39,151 --> 01:09:41,085
She talked to someone else an hour ago.

1662
01:09:41,086 --> 01:09:45,122
Then an hour later, she doesn't need
to talk to him anymore.

1663
01:09:45,390 --> 01:09:47,157
That is too casual for me.

1664
01:09:48,226 --> 01:09:50,061
Who's casual? Si Won? Yu Jin?

1665
01:09:50,062 --> 01:09:51,228
She means Yu Jin.

1666
01:09:56,668 --> 01:09:58,335
I think Si Won is nice.

1667
01:09:58,336 --> 01:10:00,137
I see.

1668
01:10:00,137 --> 01:10:02,003
He seems like a genuine guy.

1669
01:10:03,270 --> 01:10:06,537
That's basically a war without guns.

1670
01:10:07,103 --> 01:10:11,736
(A storm of emotions deepens
in the night at Yeon House.)

1671
01:10:12,103 --> 01:10:14,837
(And then comes Day 5)

1672
01:10:15,830 --> 01:10:17,263
The weather's getting pretty hot now.

1673
01:10:17,270 --> 01:10:18,103
Right?

1674
01:10:18,803 --> 01:10:21,670
Shall we go for a walk?

1675
01:10:21,970 --> 01:10:23,303
- Want to take a walk?
- Sure.

1676
01:10:23,303 --> 01:10:25,737
(Ji Seung invites Si Won
for a morning walk.)

1677
01:10:25,737 --> 01:10:26,803
- Let's go.
- Okay.

1678
01:10:27,470 --> 01:10:28,570
Here we go!

1679
01:10:28,763 --> 01:10:30,730
What are they going to talk about?
Goodness.

1680
01:10:30,737 --> 01:10:31,870
We'll see.

1681
01:10:33,303 --> 01:10:34,537
How was it for you yesterday?

1682
01:10:35,403 --> 01:10:36,270
Yesterday?

1683
01:10:37,970 --> 01:10:39,603
Yu Jin told me everything.

1684
01:10:40,170 --> 01:10:41,803
- You were still awake?
- Yeah.

1685
01:10:43,070 --> 01:10:44,370
Yu Jin suddenly said,

1686
01:10:44,370 --> 01:10:46,337
"I want to have a chat with Si Won."

1687
01:10:46,337 --> 01:10:48,170
So I told her
that you're a really nice guy.

1688
01:10:48,737 --> 01:10:50,503
I mean, you can talk, right?

1689
01:10:50,503 --> 01:10:51,537
- That's why we're here.
- True.

1690
01:10:51,537 --> 01:10:53,403
So that's why I told her that.

1691
01:10:53,403 --> 01:10:58,503
But she kept explaining why she did it.

1692
01:10:58,503 --> 01:10:59,437
So it was a bit...

1693
01:10:59,803 --> 01:11:02,103
So you feel like people are asking
for your permission...

1694
01:11:02,103 --> 01:11:03,303
to talk to me?

1695
01:11:03,303 --> 01:11:07,137
No, it's more about...

1696
01:11:07,137 --> 01:11:10,037
I heard it from Yu Jin...

1697
01:11:10,037 --> 01:11:12,303
and not from you.

1698
01:11:13,703 --> 01:11:17,303
Anyway, for me,

1699
01:11:18,265 --> 01:11:23,170
it was weird because Yu Jin wanted
to talk to Jun Han.

1700
01:11:23,170 --> 01:11:24,737
Then all of a sudden she talks with you,

1701
01:11:24,737 --> 01:11:26,903
and tells me that she doesn't need
to talk to Jun Han anymore.

1702
01:11:26,903 --> 01:11:29,837
This is basically repeating every day.

1703
01:11:30,903 --> 01:11:35,537
If I'm being honest, after we talked,

1704
01:11:35,537 --> 01:11:37,370
I was a bit more certain towards you.

1705
01:11:37,370 --> 01:11:39,803
After we talked in my room?

1706
01:11:41,037 --> 01:11:43,103
It's probably because we're different,

1707
01:11:43,103 --> 01:11:45,237
but I had a hard time understanding her.

1708
01:11:49,403 --> 01:11:51,737
- For me...
- I don't think it's weird or anything.

1709
01:11:51,737 --> 01:11:53,637
After the date yesterday,

1710
01:11:53,637 --> 01:11:56,537
Ji Hye was my first Extended Date,

1711
01:11:56,537 --> 01:11:59,003
and I had no more after that.

1712
01:11:59,003 --> 01:12:04,770
So I thought, "Maybe everyone
wants to try and talk to everyone."

1713
01:12:04,770 --> 01:12:06,403
That's what I told myself.

1714
01:12:06,403 --> 01:12:09,870
(Si Won wasn't certain
about Ji Seung's feelings.)

1715
01:12:11,103 --> 01:12:12,837
- Shouldn't we head back now?
- Now?

1716
01:12:12,837 --> 01:12:13,937
Okay.

1717
01:12:16,137 --> 01:12:18,737
(What will Si Won do
after his talk with Ji Seung?)

1718
01:12:18,737 --> 01:12:22,370
I think Ji Seung is trying to seem...

1719
01:12:22,370 --> 01:12:26,803
Like she's not in a rush,
with a fairly calm attitude.

1720
01:12:27,103 --> 01:12:30,437
But would Si Won really not see
through it?

1721
01:12:30,437 --> 01:12:32,970
- Right.
- I think he would.

1722
01:12:32,970 --> 01:12:35,303
That's really the main point.

1723
01:12:35,303 --> 01:12:37,003
It doesn't matter who says what.

1724
01:12:37,003 --> 01:12:40,137
It depends on what Si Won thinks,

1725
01:12:40,137 --> 01:12:41,403
how he evaluates her,

1726
01:12:41,403 --> 01:12:43,137
what he thinks of her,

1727
01:12:43,137 --> 01:12:45,503
and how he accepts this whole situation.

1728
01:12:45,503 --> 01:12:48,237
I think it's up to Si Won
to read the situation right.

1729
01:12:49,270 --> 01:12:52,737
(Ji Seung comes back inside
after talking with Si Won.)

1730
01:12:52,737 --> 01:12:53,637
It's so hot.

1731
01:12:54,903 --> 01:12:55,970
(Glancing)

1732
01:12:56,237 --> 01:12:57,103
Ji Seung?

1733
01:13:01,103 --> 01:13:03,503
- I had a chat with Si Won.
- Really?

1734
01:13:03,970 --> 01:13:07,737
Because it would be
weird not to in this situation.

1735
01:13:07,737 --> 01:13:08,503
Well done.

1736
01:13:12,337 --> 01:13:16,137
To be honest, I was a little surprised
when you talked to me earlier.

1737
01:13:16,137 --> 01:13:17,037
What?

1738
01:13:17,037 --> 01:13:20,203
I was a little tired...

1739
01:13:20,803 --> 01:13:23,337
and I also needed some time
to think about it.

1740
01:13:23,337 --> 01:13:25,470
But then, you...

1741
01:13:25,470 --> 01:13:26,570
She caught her off guard.

1742
01:13:26,570 --> 01:13:28,570
You weren't exactly aggressive,

1743
01:13:29,016 --> 01:13:30,983
and you were trying to be considerate.

1744
01:13:31,803 --> 01:13:34,470
But instead of just telling me
what happened,

1745
01:13:34,470 --> 01:13:37,937
you were informing me
about what you will do from now on.

1746
01:13:39,437 --> 01:13:43,137
So it seemed like I was telling you
that I'm going for Si Won now.

1747
01:13:43,137 --> 01:13:45,903
Yes, so it felt like you were
declaring war against me.

1748
01:13:45,903 --> 01:13:47,403
That's what it felt like to me.

1749
01:13:47,403 --> 01:13:50,703
I think that's why you felt that way.

1750
01:13:52,470 --> 01:13:54,437
Here's what I meant.

1751
01:13:54,437 --> 01:13:57,370
I was just talking about that situation.

1752
01:13:57,370 --> 01:13:59,937
I wasn't declaring war.

1753
01:13:59,937 --> 01:14:05,837
Of course, you're free to express
what you feel.

1754
01:14:06,303 --> 01:14:07,970
That's just what I was thinking.

1755
01:14:07,970 --> 01:14:10,003
I don't want to be on bad terms with you.

1756
01:14:10,003 --> 01:14:13,370
- Me neither. Not at all.
- So I wanted to talk about it.

1757
01:14:14,103 --> 01:14:17,637
(Where will Si Won's heart head towards?)

1758
01:14:17,903 --> 01:14:19,037
This one looks nice.

1759
01:14:19,703 --> 01:14:20,670
You're so cute.

1760
01:14:22,103 --> 01:14:23,037
I really enjoyed it.

1761
01:14:24,270 --> 01:14:26,237
I think my feelings grew.

1762
01:14:26,870 --> 01:14:28,603
Our photos look amazing.

1763
01:14:28,603 --> 01:14:30,003
You're really pretty.

1764
01:14:30,003 --> 01:14:31,903
Si Won is really handsome.

1765
01:14:33,037 --> 01:14:34,670
It bothered me a little.

1766
01:14:35,203 --> 01:14:38,070
I'm not saying that I don't
see you as a man.

1767
01:14:38,403 --> 01:14:40,403
If I'm being honest,
there was chemistry today.

1768
01:14:42,270 --> 01:14:43,837
I don't think I'll be able to focus...

1769
01:14:43,837 --> 01:14:45,570
because I'm so conflicted.

1770
01:14:45,837 --> 01:14:47,237
But do I need to hear more?

1771
01:14:47,237 --> 01:14:48,670
I thought I made your heart flutter
a bit today.

1772
01:14:53,337 --> 01:14:54,937
(Pandora's QR is now open.)

1773
01:14:54,937 --> 01:14:56,927
(If you scan the QR code
of the person you're curious about,)

1774
01:14:56,928 --> 01:14:58,703
(you'll be able to check
who their top pick is.)

1775
01:14:59,503 --> 01:15:01,770
(Pandora's QR appears at Yeon House.)

1776
01:15:02,170 --> 01:15:05,103
(They enter the QR Room to find out
how their crush really feels.)

1777
01:15:05,403 --> 01:15:06,737
I was curious.

1778
01:15:07,870 --> 01:15:09,103
(Squinting)

1779
01:15:10,570 --> 01:15:11,937
I definitely wanted to see it.

1780
01:15:12,370 --> 01:15:13,703
What did you and Ji Hye talk about?

1781
01:15:14,203 --> 01:15:16,003
I want you to be a bit more
curious about me.

1782
01:15:16,003 --> 01:15:18,937
I decided to go all in for you.

1783
01:15:21,503 --> 01:15:22,870
How do you feel now?

1784
01:15:23,603 --> 01:15:25,470
I'm certain.

1785
01:15:25,470 --> 01:15:26,603
Certain about what?

1786
01:15:27,770 --> 01:15:30,370
I'll enter the door in your heart.

1787
01:15:30,370 --> 01:15:31,837
(Blushing)

1788
01:15:32,603 --> 01:15:34,423
(What change will Pandora's QR bring
to the Yeon House?)

1789
01:15:34,530 --> 01:15:35,690
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
